roducts. The product has the appearance of etched glass. It’s also more durable, lighter and easier to work with than glass.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Frosted Acrylic Signs by Shape</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can order frosted acrylic signs in custom shapes. However, we offer a few popular options to facilitate the design process.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Square or Rectangle</strong> - 90° angles with pointed corners</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Rounded</strong> - 90° angles with rounded corners at 1/4\"-1/2\" radius</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Outline</strong> - custom shape</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Overline - </strong>custom shape with an extra non-printed border of frosted acrylic</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Printing of Frosted Acrylic Signs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frosted acrylic signs can be printed in full color like regular <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-signs/\">acrylic signs</a>. Your design is directly printed on the front side of the material. The printed surface loses its etched effect while the remaining part retains the frosted appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material of Frosted Acrylic Signs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The material we use is clear acrylic with an etched surface on one side. This effect obscures the view but allows light transmission.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Choose from the two material thickness options for your frosted acrylic sign: 1/8\" (0.125\") or 1/4\" (0.25\"). While the 1/8\" option makes even large signs durable, you’re free to choose the thickness you like.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mounting of Frosted Acrylic Signs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer silver and gold standoff mounting for frosted acrylic signs. The metal standoffs will be visible and give your sign a professional look. Choose from the two sizes of standoffs, 1/2\" (0.5\") or 1\", and use the option to have drilled holes if you need them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>*Please note that you should select the drilled holes and standoff options from the design tool before finalizing your order.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Use our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\">design tool</a> and upload your own design or choose one of our free templates. Our platform gives you the freedom to personalize your frosted acrylic signage to meet your requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>','<h1><strong>Installation Guide for Frosted Acrylic Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer standoff mounting for frosted acrylic signs. For installation, you’ll need a screwdriver, drill (if you choose to make the holes yourself), anchors and the standoffs with all included parts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Choose a level surface and mark the areas for drilling the holes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Drill the holes and insert the anchors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You may skip the first two steps if you get the holes pre-drilled by selecting the option in our design tool.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Screw the standoff barrels onto the anchors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Align the drilled holes of the frosted acrylic sign with the barrels on the wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Screw in the caps of the standoffs to sandwich the print between the barrels and the caps</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Frosted Acrylic Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1/8\"(0.125\"), 1/4\"(0.25\") </p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Material finish:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Frosted</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.75lbs/sqft, 1.2lbs/sqft</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Drilled hole options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>four corners, top and bottom center, top corners only, four corners and top and bottom center, right & left center drilled holes</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min․ size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Silver or gold standoffs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max. size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>48\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Full-color digital printing with fade-resistant inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>18\"x18\", 18\"x24\", 18\"x36\", 24\"x24\", 24\"x36\", 24\"x48\", 36\"x36\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard printing</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Shape:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Rectangle, square, any custom shape</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, rounded, overline or outline</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Material color:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Clear</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan outdoors:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+ years outdoors, 15+ years indoors</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',48.00,96.00,4.00,4.00,NULL,0,0,241.109478,0.242687,NULL),(4,'Aluminum Signs','Aluminum signs are durable and long-lasting, making them a favored choice. This resilience stems from aluminum\'s inherent properties; it is a metal that resists corrosion and withstands harsh weather conditions.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71UL7+di08L._SX522_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81BApwzEuUL._SX522_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41KO0VRtkDL._SL1500_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61zN-hiUQcL._SX522_.jpg','inches',1,'<h2><strong>Aluminum Signs Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you want to enhance your space for decorative, business, or promotional purposes? Order custom aluminum signs to stand apart from your competitors. Our aluminum signs are the best since they&rsquo;re:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rust-proof</li>\r\n	<li>UV-safe</li>\r\n	<li>Durable</li>\r\n	<li>Weather-resistant</li>\r\n	<li>Super handy</li>\r\n	<li>Long-lasting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Create your aluminum sign with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">Brand Experts</a>&nbsp;to spruce up your interior and exterior design. Your&nbsp;custom signs&nbsp;will strike awe in everyone who sees them. We ship products all across the UAE . Check our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">terms and policies page</a>&nbsp;to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Products Related to Custom Aluminum Signs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/30\">Brushed aluminum signs</a>&nbsp;offer extra appeal thanks to their polished faces. They&rsquo;re commonly used as a modern interior solution in the workplace or the house.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/105\">Metal photo prints</a>&nbsp;are decorative aluminum signs designed to enhance any space with a stylish touch. Large photos and illustrations are applied to the plaques to create gorgeous showpieces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/5\">Dibond signs</a>&nbsp;are innovative aluminum signs with two metal layers sandwiching a rigid core. They&rsquo;re used in various weather conditions and are ideal for art exhibitions and festivals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://brandexperts.ae/product/5\">Reflective aluminum signs</a>&nbsp;are the most optimal solution for caution plaques. The front face is coated with reflective vi