 long-lasting, ideally preventing any impacts that may result from harsh weather.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51+WUg4CuxL._SX342_SY445_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81IYzc-NwRL._SX522_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81vQqq3wtzL._SX522_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81-BKUgc0AL._SX522_.jpg','inches',1,'<h2><strong>Dibond Signs Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Dibond signs which are also known as composite aluminum signs, are among the toughest and most resilient <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/category/metal-signs/\">metal signs</a> available. They’re very versatile and durable, making them suitable for a wide array of applications. Dibond signs can be utilized in creating anything from regulatory street displays to appealing wall art pieces for exhibitions. Harnessing the strength of two robust metal layers either side of a sturdy plastic, dibond signs are more reliable and less flexible than <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/aluminum-signs/\">aluminum signs</a>. Still, dibond signs are lighter, bend-resistant and long-lasting, ideally preventing any impacts that may result from harsh weather.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/\">Square Signs</a> offers composite aluminum signs with a series of tools and the possibility to personalize the plaques. We offer shipping across the US and Canada. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Dibond Signs by Usage</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Dibond signs are a great recommendation for promotional, decorative and many other purposes. Get to know the most popular usages listed below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Dibond Logo Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Composite aluminum signs will help you amplify your brand voice with an elegantly printed trademark. Create your dibond sign for exterior or interior showcasing. Choose its form, customize it so that it matches your vision and order it within a couple of minutes. The sturdy, smooth-looking dibond sign will provide your office with a professional look.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Promotional Dibond Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/ds-1.jpg\" style=\"height:338px; width:600px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you need an innovative touch to improve your business voice? You can safely bet that dibond signs are the product to make it happen. To generate more walk-ins, think of new and unique designs and graphics for your dibond signs that’ll make them catchier by restyling them. Thanks to their impressive sturdiness and premium quality, the laser-cut dibond signs are used under different weather conditions. Restaurants, beauty salons, and construction sites are just some of the few places that can boost their advertising with these elegant displays, perfectly complemented by <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/foamboard-signs/\">foam board signs</a> for indoor promotions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Dibond Name Plates</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Elegance and professionalism are key when it comes to enterprises. Employees’ work attire, office desks and smoothly designed office walls can all look even better if you add some attractive accessories such as metal name plates. Dibond signs are your go to solution in this case. Order small composite name plates with personalized graphics. </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Directional Dibond Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Gradually-developing experiential design grows more sophisticated and integrates premium quality products for directional projects.Dibond signs, just like <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-signs/\">custom acrylic signs</a>, are the lead products here. Since wayfinding systems are designed for exterior and interior use, dibond aluminum signs match all needs guaranteeing a smooth look and high endurance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our services will help you make your dibond signs online with the help of our easy-to-use <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\">sign design tool</a>. You’ll get your choice in shape, background colors and many other details to create the perfect display for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Regulatory Dibond Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Dibond signs are among the metal products that have been predominantly used outside as traffic, safety and other road-related displays. The necessity of safety guides and traffic-regulating displays never dwindles. So create yours from Alu-dibond prints and use them for the upcoming five years and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Dibond Printing</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Despite their rough look, dibond aluminum prints can captivate with their vivid visuals and even surfaces. The changeable custom dibond signs are utilized in both their free-standing and wall-mounted versions. Learn how to use ACM panel signs to decorate your home and office walls.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Dibond Photo Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/ds-2.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you preparing to organize an exhibition for your own artwork? You can think of dibond photo printing as a fresh suggestion for this event. Our custom dibond signs are available in various forms. Get them fully colored with your artwork and set them up as free-standing displays on any flat surface or mount them onto the walls. Either variant will accentuate the vividness of the dibond photo printing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Decorative Dibond Prints</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Dibond photo printing is a fresh solution for interior decoration. You have the ability to create vivid patterns or full pictures to use as graphics on the product. Go to our collection of designer-made <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">templates</a> and pick from the hundreds of templates available. Restyle the templates by modifying texts, background colors, adding icons and otherwise customizing every aspect of your dibond photo printing you can imagine. Your dibond sign will be large enough yet very lightweight for an easy installation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Popular Sizes for Custom Dibond Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12”x24”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>18”x24”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>18”x36”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>24”x48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>48”x48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>36”x72”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Price</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$33.18</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$42.27</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$55.9</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$87.71</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$160.41</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$178.59</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Our custom dibond signs range from 4”x4” to 96”x48”. In this chart you can find the prices for popular sizes of this product without extra options and installation accessories.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>* The prices in this chart may be outdated. To check the current prices and discounts for this product, please refer to the calculator at the top of the page.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Main Features of Dibond Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Learn all the technical details of custom dibond signs before buying them. Be sure that the dibond signs will satisfy your requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Material and Printing Options for Dibond Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/ds-3.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A composite aluminum sign is a super rigid and tough product that is rust and bend-resistant. Lighter than pure aluminum, a dibond sign originally comes with two thin, solid aluminum panels tightly bonded with a polyethylene core. The front and back surfaces can have a white or brushed silver coating, letting the ink sit smoothly. This composite sign board is the best product to withstand weather conditions such as snow, rain and heat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For dibond printing, we use full-color UV curing printers. Inks are applied and dried with UV rays making the graphics sun-resistant. The color vividness won’t fade away when placed under the sun and will retain its initial look. We offer two types of dibond signs printing: single-sided and double-sided.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Single-sided</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>With single-sided dibond sign printing the image is applied only to the front surface. It’s an ideal solution for wall-mounted dibond signs.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Double-sided</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Double-sided dibond aluminum printing will increase the visual effectiveness of the plaque. The graphics are applied on both sides making a unique free-standing or hanging display.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Shapes of Custom Dibond Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>CNC cutting routers will help you get custom dibond signs. The machines are controlled by software, ensuring high accuracy and preventing substance waste. Dibond signs are cut into all possible shapes. Thanks to its durability, your dibond sign will come in the precise model ordered by you. Also keep in mind that we don’t provide cut-out options.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Square and Rectangle</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The dibond sign is cut in standard square or rectangle shapes with pointed corners. Be careful not to harm yourself with the sharp corners during installation.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rounded</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The dibond printing is cut in a square or rectangular shape of the selected sizes. With this option, the corners are rounded and smoothed to give a polished look to the dibond signs.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Outline</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Outline cutting forms the dibond sign with the selected design. You are free to choose any form for your dibond printing while creating it on our design platform.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Overline</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The custom dibond signs come in an outline cut, but with an extra border surrounding them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Installation of Custom Dibond Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/ds-4.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide several options for setting up dibond signs along with their installation accessories. Please note that the accessories will add to the cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Stand-offs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Stand-off mounting is the most common installation method for dibond signs. Set up the display by fixing it to the wall with the bolts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>*Please note that you should select the drilled holes and standoff options from the design tool before finalizing your order for dibond signs.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Easel Backs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This option is preferred for free-standing dibond signs. Order them with easel backs and let them stand on flat furniture. It’s a perfect idea for setting up your dibond photo printing.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Zip Ties</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Fixing custom dibond signs with zip ties works ideally when you need to mount them onto metal wire fences as caution posters.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Command Strips</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want an invisible mounting method for your dibond photo printing, choose command strips. The strips stick to the back of the display and the adhesives will prevent it from falling off.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Suction Cup and Hook</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>It works perfectly for double-sided dibond printing to be installed on glass doors, windows, etc... Again, the dibond signs come with premade holes and installation accessories in the package.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison Chart of Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p> </p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Dibond Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/brushed-aluminum-signs/\"><strong>Brushed Aluminum Signs</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/reflective-aluminum-signs/\"><strong>Reflective Aluminum Signs</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/metal-photo-prints/\"><strong>Metal Photo Prints</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-photo-prints/\"><strong>Acrylic Photo Prints</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size range</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4”x4” - 96”x48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4”x4” - 96”x48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4”x4” - 96”x48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4”x4” - 96”x48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4”x4” - 96”x48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.125\"<br />\r\n			0.25”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.032\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.125\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.125\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.125\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single-sided</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Double-sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single-sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single-sided</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Double-sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single-sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Second-surface</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (outdoors/indoors)</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+/10+</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>10+/15+</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+/10+</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>10+/15+</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+/15+</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Dibond Signs FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What is a dibond sign?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>A dibond sign is a rigid product with two metal faces and a plastic core. It’s stronger than epanel and lighter than standard aluminum. For more information, check out our dibond signs specification page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How long can I use my dibond signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Dibond signs are generally sturdy products which can be used outdoors like <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/corrugated-plastic-signs/\">corrugated plastic signs</a>, but their lifespan differs based on installation area. They can withstand more than five years outside and ten years indoors.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How do I care for my dibond sign?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Wipe your dibond sign regularly with a cotton towel and lukewarm water. Please note that any acid or alcohol-based liquid will wipe off the dibond printing and damage the plaque.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How do I install my dibond signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide several ways to set up dibond signs. Mount them onto walls or keep them free-standing on flat areas such as tables, mantels and countertops with the necessary accessories. Find more details on our dibond signs installation page</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>','<h1><strong>Installation of Dibond Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom dibond signs are ideal for exterior and interior applications. Follow these quick steps to install your dibond signs with their respective installation accessories.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easel Backs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easel backs are lightweight, self-adhesive cardboard stands for displaying dibond signs on tables or countertops. Use as many easel backs as needed depending on the size and weight of the sign. For aluminum composite signs, we recommend using easel backs only for smaller displays.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Take one of the easel backs and fold the wing inward to cut open the pre-dotted area. Repeat the same action with the other easel back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Fold down the circular easel stabilizer and secure easel wings in the slot.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Peel off the tapes from the adhesive bands on both easel backs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Position the adhesive parts of the easel backs on both sides of the sign and press for a few seconds to make sure they are securely fixed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We’re done. Now you are ready to display your small dibond signs on any flat surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Command Strips</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Command strips will arrive in pairs already attached to the back of the sign. The strips consist of two identical layers that ‘click’ together. One side of the strip is covered with an adhesive layer and the other with hooks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before the installation, clean the area of application for secure adhesion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Measure out the area of application and mark the spot where you want to install the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Take the sign with command strips already attached to it and peel the backing paper off the strips.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Press the dibond sign with the strips against the surface in the pre-marked position. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>To ensure the adhesive will hold, remove the sign from its bottom corners, pulling it up and away from the surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Now, press the strips onto the wall for a few seconds to ensure that they are secure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Wait about an hour before reattaching the frame, to make sure the strips are securely attached to the surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7:</strong> Align the strips on the sign with the strips on the wall.  Press the sign onto the wall until each pair of strips click and seal into place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We’re done. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>In case you need to remove the sign, grab its bottom corners, then pull it up and away from the surface. Finally, remove the strips by pulling them downward.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zip Ties</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> First, you need to find the perfect location and a fitted object for the zip tie installation. Position the holes of the sign into place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Take one zip tie and pass it through one of the drilled holes on the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Now, thread the zip tie through the hole and around the object to be secured on. Pull the zip tie to tighten it around the sign and the object.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Take the scissors and cut the extra end of the zip tie for a cleaner look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5: </strong>Repeat the same action with the rest of the applicable corners of the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We’re done. The sign is now securely fixed into place from two or four corners as needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Suction Cup and Hook</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Take the suction cup and press it firmly into place, making sure there are no air bubbles between the cup and the mounting surface.   </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Once the suction cup is securely fixed into place, take the sign with the rope and hang it from the hook.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>We’re done. The suction cup and hook are securely fixed in place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For heavier dibond signs, use two suction cups.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Standoffs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Required tools:</strong> Standoffs, a drill, screws, anchors, marker and measuring tape</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Standoffs include an anchor, screw, barrel and a cap with a threaded stud. The anchor is used to fix the standoff to the wall. The standoff barrel is what spaces the sign at a desired distance from the wall. Then, the threaded stud is used to sandwich the sign with the cap which adds a decorative finish to the wall-mounted sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Preparation:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before the installation, take the measuring tape and find the perfect position for the installation. Take the sign with pre-drilled holes and place it on the wall. Using the holes on the sign as a guide, mark the areas of the standoffs on the wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Drill 4 holes in the marked areas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Install the anchors, leaving enough external threading to allow the barrel to attach to the exposed end.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Now, take the barrel and screw it to the wall via the anchor. Repeat the same action with the rest of the barrels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>Next, take the sign and line up the holes with the standoffs on the wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Take the caps with the threaded studs and fasten the sign on the standoffs. This will sandwich the sign between the barrel and the cap.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We’re done. The sign is now securely mounted to the wall with standoffs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>','<h1><strong>Specifications Of Dibond Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Material:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Polyethylene core between two thin aluminum sheets</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Smooth, sun and deformation-resistant, substitute for standard aluminum</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.125”,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>0.25”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standoffs, suction cup & hook, command strips, zip ties and easel backs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.765 lbs/ft2,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>1.53 lbs/ft2</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Digital, high resolution - full color with UV inks, graphics can be single or double-sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard white,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Brushed silver</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Drilled Hole Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 corners, top and bottom center, top corners only, 4 corners and top and bottom center</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size Range:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4”x4” - 48\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, overline or outline, rounded</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12”x18”, 24”x36\", 18\"x24\", 18\"x36\", 24\"x24\", 24\"x48\", custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (Indoors/Outdoors):</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>10+ / 5+ years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>',60.00,120.00,4.00,4.00,NULL,0,0,59.719921,0.284302,NULL),(6,'Vinyl Banners','Vinyl banners are an ideal advertising tool for different events. These lightweight items feature stellar imagery to make an impression.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/615L9Fm1F6L._SX522_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61WXAp4L1OL.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51FjDy3PMAL.jpg','https:/