special sales to seasonal offers and new product launches. These&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/33\">business banners</a>&nbsp;will draw in foot traffic, placed either at storefronts or in busy shopping areas. Order your vinyl banners online and leverage our fast delivery service across the UAE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/hanging-birthday-vinyl-banner.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Celebrations and Milestones</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Print vinyl poster displays to introduce a festive flair to your celebrations and milestones. Vinyl banners can showcase personalized messages and illustrations, making any occasion &mdash; be it a birthday party, graduation or an anniversary &mdash; memorable. Create your unique vinyl banner using our&nbsp;sign design tool&nbsp;and celebrate your life achievements. Use our templates to save time on designing your custom vinyl banners.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/hanging-outdoor-vinyl-banner-real-estate.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Trade Shows and Exhibitions</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Vinyl posters are a must-have when it comes to highlighting company names, logos and services at trade shows and exhibitions. Products such as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/25\">X-stand banners</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/24\">step and repeat banners</a>&nbsp;help businesses stand out at trade show booths. Make the most out of such crowded events with printed vinyl banners. These high-quality marketing tools attract potential customers, convey professionalism, and leave a lasting impression.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/vinyl-banners-for-sports-event.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Sports Competitions and Tournaments</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Fuel the competitive spirit with custom vinyl banners for sports events. Spread the word and invite people to a championship with appealing designs tailored to your needs. Perfect for individual tournaments, marathons, or track and field meets, these items will promote your event and highlight key sponsors. Let your event stand out with striking banners that inspire athletes and captivate audiences. Durable and weather-resistant, they&rsquo;ll hold up throughout rain and shine. Opt for large options to maximize your visibility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/vinyl-banners-for-holidays.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Seasonal and Holiday Events</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Create buzz and excitement for your special events with vinyl banners that echo the warmth of the holiday season. Capture passersby&rsquo;s attention with vibrant colors, festive themes, and catchy messages. Whether promoting a winter market, holiday concert, or community festival, these marketing tools set the tone for celebration. Designed to withstand harsh weather conditions, they&rsquo;re perfect for indoor and outdoor applications. Make your event unforgettable by creating a joyful atmosphere with these effective advertising tools.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/vinyl-banners-for-fundraising-charity-events.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Fundraising and Charity Events</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Support your cause by incorporating vinyl banners into your fundraising and charity events. Bold and engaging designs will help draw attention to your mission and inspire community involvement. Whether you&#39;re promoting a silent auction, a fun run, or a donation drive, vinyl banner printing ensures a professional look that reflects your dedication. Built to last, these media are perfect for spreading your message far and wide. Make an impact with a vinyl banner that motivates and unites people for a meaningful cause.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/designing-process-of-vinyl-banners.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Templates for Vinyl Banners</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Explore our extensive library of&nbsp;sign templates&nbsp;to jumpstart the creation process of your vinyl banner. With a variety of themes available, you can easily find the one that serves a solid foundation to build upon and fulfill any purpose.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOnce you&rsquo;ve selected a template, make it uniquely yours by customizing every detail. Feel free to experiment with colors, images, fonts, and texts to align the design with your vision. Craft a striking vinyl banner and make an impact on your audience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Specifications Of Custom Vinyl Banner</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"32\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/face-material.png\" width=\"32\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Face</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13 mil thick PVC</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"32\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/uv-printing.png\" width=\"32\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>full-color UV printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"32\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/lifespan.png\" width=\"32\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lifespan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5+ years indoors, 3+ outdoors</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"358\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/printing-of-vinyl-banners.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Printing and Material of Custom Vinyl Banners</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our UV-curing machines help us print vinyl poster illustrations that maintain vibrancy even under prolonged sun exposure. These one-sided products can last over five years with proper care.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer two finishing options for vinyl banner printing: flush-cut and hemmed edges. Flush-cut vinyl posters have standard, single-layer edges, while hemmed banners feature sewn edges that enhance durability and wind resistance. Both options ensure that your vinyl banner printing remains appealing in any setting.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCustom vinyl banners are a top industry product known for versatility and convenience. This medium is made of a white 13-mil-thick, soft, lightweight PVC layer. Its waterproof and abrasion-resistant feature makes it perfect for displaying large messages like&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/17\">outdoor banners</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How To Set Up Custom Vinyl Banners</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>How to Hang a Vinyl Banner With Zip Ties?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>*Insert a zip tie through each grommet.</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/zip-ties-step-1-and-2.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 1</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Pass the zip tie around the support structure (fence, pole, etc.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/zip-ties-step-3.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 2</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Fix the vinyl banner with grommets moving from top to bottom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/zip-ties-step-4.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 3</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Cut the remaining edge of the zip tie with pliers and ensure the custom vinyl poster is securely attached.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How to Hang a Vinyl Poster With Hanging Clips?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/hanging-clips-step-1.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 1</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Install the hanging clips on the support structure (fence,pole,etc.).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/hanging-clips-step-2.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 2</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Attach the clips to the vinyl banner with grommets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/hanging-clips-step-3-and-4.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 3</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ensure the poster is evenly supported by all clips.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How to Hang a Print Vinyl Poster With Pole Pockets?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/pole-pockets-step-1.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 1</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Open the pole pockets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/pole-pockets-step-2.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 2</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Insert the pole through the pockets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/pole-pockets-step-3.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 3</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Secure the poles at the installation spot.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Vinyl Banners FAQ</h3>\r\n\r\n<h4>What Are Vinyl Banners Made Of?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>They&rsquo;re made from a soft PVC (polyvinyl chloride) material. It&#39;s durable, weather-resistant and suitable for outdoor use.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>How Long Do Printed Vinyl Banners Last Outdoors?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The lifespan of a custom vinyl banner outdoors depends on several factors such as weather conditions and regular care. Our high-quality vinyl posters can last 3-5 years when properly maintained.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Can I Install A Vinyl Banner Myself?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, you can install it yourself. Make sure you have the right tools and follow proper installation techniques to secure it properly. Here&rsquo;s how to hang a vinyl banner outside or inside. Choose a clean, visible location with anchor points. Measure and mark points for the grommets. Install hooks or stakes if needed. Thread rope or bungee cords through the grommets and secure to the points. Alternatively, use zip ties, looped through grommets and tightened. Ensure that it&rsquo;s taut and secure in all corners.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>How To Clean A Vinyl Banner?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Use lukewarm water mixed with mild soap or detergent to thoroughly clean your vinyl banner. Gently scrub the vinyl banner printing with a soft cloth or sponge, then rinse it with clean water. Avoid using harsh chemicals or abrasive scrubbers as they can damage the banner&#39;s surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>How To Guarantee Durability For Custom Vinyl Banners In Harsh Weather Conditions?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Install printed vinyl banners&nbsp;well to ensure they withstand strong winds and harsh weather conditions. Regularly inspect for wear and tear, promptly repairing any damage. Hemming the vinyl banner printing&nbsp;adds strength and extends its lifespan.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>How To Remove Wrinkles From A Vinyl Banner?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Lay it flat in a warm and sunny area. Stretch the custom vinyl poster gently or use a hair dryer on low heat to smooth out wrinkles effectively. Avoid using high heat or applying excessive force. This could permanently harm the custom vinyl poster&nbsp;material.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>How to Properly Store Vinyl Banners?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Roll your banner with the printed side facing out to protect the inks and prevent creases or wrinkles. Store it in the box it was shipped in for safekeeping. Avoid exposing your vinyl banner to extreme heat or direct sunlight to prevent rapid fading.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Do Vinyl Banners Fade Over Time?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>They can fade over time when exposed to heat or rain. Yet, with the proper care and maintenance, they are guaranteed to last for 3 to 5 years.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Can I Create a Double-Sided Vinyl Banner?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>No, our vinyl banners are available with a single-sided printing option only.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<h3>Step 1</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Pass the zip tie around the support structure (fence, pole, etc.)</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 2</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Fix the vinyl banner with grommets moving from top to bottom.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 3</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Cut the remaining edge of the zip tie with pliers and ensure the custom vinyl poster is securely attached.</p>','<h2>Specifications Of Custom Vinyl Banner</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"32\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/face-material.png\" width=\"32\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Face</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13 mil thick PVC</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"32\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/uv-printing.png\" width=\"32\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>full-color UV printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"32\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/lifespan.png\" width=\"32\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lifespan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5+ years indoors, 3+ outdoors</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"358\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/01/printing-of-vinyl-banners.jpg\" width=\"518\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Printing and Material of Custom Vinyl Banners</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our UV-curing machines help us print vinyl poster illustrations that maintain vibrancy even under prolonged sun exposure. These one-sided products can last over five years with proper care.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer two finishing options for vinyl banner printing: flush-cut and hemmed edges. Flush-cut vinyl posters have standard, single-layer edges, while hemmed banners feature sewn edges that enhance durability and wind resistance. Both options ensure that your vinyl banner printing remains appealing in any setting.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCustom vinyl banners are a top industry product known for versatility and convenience. This medium is made of a white 13-mil-thick, soft, lightweight PVC layer. Its waterproof and abrasion-resistant feature makes it perfect for displaying large messages like&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/17\">outdoor banners</a>.</p>',1680.00,120.00,12.00,11.00,NULL,0,0,42.501025,0.063079,NULL),(7,'PVC Signs','Install lightweight and high quality PVC signs indoors or outdoors. They’re great for decoration, branding and much more.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51QNI5dZY2L._SL1100_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51nrXVKvASL._SX522_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61KXkYPI20L._SX522_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61KXkYPI20L._SX522_.jpg','inches',NULL,'<h2><strong>PVC Signs Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you looking for a light, versatile, affordable and high quality display? PVC signs meet all those criteria. Though similar in appearance, the product differs from <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/foamboard-signs/\">foam board printing</a>. It’s made entirely of plastic as opposed to a rigid foam sandwiched between two sheets of paper. These PVC board signs are convenient for various purposes. PVC signs can be used both indoors and outdoors for different occasions. A PVC poster is ideal for everything from personal decoration to business branding. PVC prints have several benefits, some of which are listed below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lightweight</li>\r\n	<li>Cost effective</li>\r\n	<li>Waterproof</li>\r\n	<li>Rigid but bendy</li>\r\n	<li>High durability</li>\r\n	<li>Smooth surface</li>\r\n	<li>Double-sided option</li>\r\n	<li>Direct UV printing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Create your custom PVC signs online with <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/\">Square Signs</a>. We’ll ensure that you get top quality products with premium printing on PVC boards. Order your <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/custom-signs/\">custom signs</a> now and enjoy fast shipping all across the US and Canada.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>PVC Board Signs by Usage</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A PVC sign is a multipurpose medium with a vast range of benefits. One of the top features of PVC board signs is the ability to display graphics on both sides of your PVC prints. PVC signs can be placed both indoors and outdoors for whatever purpose you require. You can make PVC board signs to show people directions, decorate, share information and beyond.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Directional PVC Prints</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/pvcs-1.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>PVC board signs, just like <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/aluminum-signs/\">aluminum signs</a> and <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/corrugated-plastic-signs/\">corrugated plastic signs</a>, are waterproof and perfect for guiding people to their destinations. Use them for wayfinding to bathrooms, parking lots, stores, offices and beyond. PVC poster printing is also ideal for showing off maps, directories or floor plans for visitors. You can also use them to display addresses, property names, vacancies and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Informative PVC Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/pvcs-2.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Use PVC signs to disseminate any kind of information. The displays can be made in sizes ranging from 4”x4” to 48”x96”. You can make them as small and large as you need to get your message across. Take into consideration where you’ll be placing the PVC poster to decide on an appropriate size. A large PVC sign, for example, can be placed on the face of a school building so that students can see it when gathered outside. Smaller PVC signs may be used as decorative desk displays.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Decorative PVC Poster Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/pvcs-3.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The good thing about PVC signs is that you can print anything you like on them and use the product for your home as well as your business. If you want to spruce up the kitchen, bedroom or even an office, just pick a design and we’ll take care of the PVC board printing for you. Leave everyone in awe with high resolution and fade-resistant images for decorative or promotional purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Promotional PVC Prints</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>PVC signs have a smooth surface that takes on vibrant images. Many brands use them to promote and advertise their products and services. PVC prints are a very affordable medium for businesses that need to keep their advertising costs down. Installing PVC board signs with a product’s image and listing its features and benefits can drive sales and expand your audience with minimal expenditure.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Custom PVC Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the functions listed above, PVC signs can serve a multitude of other purposes. The material is very versatile with customization options. PVC prints can take on any graphic, text and shape you desire, come in a wide range of sizes and can be installed in several ways.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>PVC Prints by Location</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>PVC prints can achieve various goals based on common locations of usage. PVC signs are suitable both indoors and outdoors. They can last around 10 years when placed inside and more than three years outside. Custom PVC signs are fully waterproof and the material’s even used for piping. Let’s see where these products are often found.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Restaurant PVC Prints</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/pvcs-4.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Restaurants use PVC signs for several reasons. Many restaurants display their menus outdoors on PVC board signs in order to attract tourists and passersby. Some restaurants also hand out individual menus on plastic sheets. The material protects the menu from tearing and spillage, reducing waste and preserving its prime appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Real Estate PVC Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Many construction companies use PVC signs to display images of architecture in progress or projects they’ve built over the years. Companies also use <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-photo-prints/\">acrylic photo prints</a> to showcase HD graphics of the spaces they’ve designed. Even more commonly, realtors place PVC board signs in the yard of the property they’re working with to attract renters and buyers. They even hang PVC poster printing on the home or building facades to make their offers more visible.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Office PVC Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Corporate offices use PVC signs to adorn their headquarters with high-res graphics. Just like <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/metal-photo-prints/\">metal photo prints</a>, they can really spruce up a space. Whether they apply these products for decorative or branding purposes, PVC poster signs accomplish the objective with style. Custom PVC signs are lightweight products that have a high quality and are easy to mount. Use them to display motivational texts and images to boost morale and productivity.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Trade Show PVC Prints</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Companies look to attract as much attention as possible during trade shows. They bring their A-game to maximize the exposure of their brand and reach the right audience. In this type of environment, quantity matters as much as quality. Take advantage of the inexpensive quality of PVC signs. Place as many as you can in different locations to increase visibility and catch the eye of people passing by.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>PVC Board Printing Options</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We use a direct printing method for our PVC signs. This means that we apply inks directly onto the material as opposed to applying a layer of vinyl or paper over it for the design. This method reduces the chance of the face of your product getting torn or peeling off. We also apply our inks with a UV-curing system. This process dries the inks with ultraviolet light, making the PVC board printing fade-resistant and longer-lasting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can order single-sided or double-sided PVC board printing. The single-sided option is better if you want to attach your PVC prints to a wall or if you intend to have it facing just one way. As for the double-sided option, it’s ideal for displays that will be suspended from the ceiling or hanging in any other way that would leave both sides visible. The second option will double your visibility. We will automatically print the same design on the front and back sides of the PVC prints if you opt for this option. However, you can contact our specialists if you want to have different graphics displayed on each side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We also offer custom PVC printing services, which means you can get PVC sign printing in any style, shape or design you can imagine. Head over to our user-friendly <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\">design tool</a> and create your PVC prints with just a few clicks. You can upload ready-made designs to our tool and adjust them if need be. You may also modify our collection of original <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">templates</a> which are free for you to use. Add texts, elements and backgrounds to make the graphics match your vision. Once you’re done with the design, select options such as the number of drilled holes and installation accessories. Choose all the add-ons you need and order your PVC signs online in a matter of minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Cutting Options for PVC Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We use a CNC router to cut our PVC signs. This state-of-the-art machine cuts the material with pinpoint accuracy to reduce material waste and ensure that the product has perfect edges. For thinner, custom cut PVC signs, we offer laser cutting to yield any design with precision. Rather than cutting the PVC board signs with a spindle like the CNC router, this machine burns through the material, giving it smoother edges. We offer four different cutting options for our PVC prints.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Square / Rectangle Cut</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This cutting option will give your PVC sign printing a standard square or rectangular shape with pointed 90-degree corners.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rounded Cut</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If you choose this option, your PVC board printing will be similar to a standard square or rectangular cut, but the corners will be rounded and smooth.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Outline Cut</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This option will give you custom cut PVC signs in the exact outline shape of your design without any borders around it.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Overline Cut</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This option will also give you custom cut PVC signs, but with a thin black or white border running around your design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Material Specifications for PVC Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>PVC, or polyvinyl chloride, is a durable, waterproof and high-quality plastic material used for various purposes in different industries. Our PVC signs come in either black or white but you can choose any color backgrounds, texts or graphics for your PVC board printing. Whether you opt for a white PVC sign or a black PVC sign, they’re both perfect for decorative, branding, informational and wayfinding purposes among others. Note that while these products are more bendable than <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-signs/\">acrylic signs</a>, you shouldn’t force them to fold or they will break.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Mounting Options for PVC Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>There are several ways for you to mount your custom PVC prints both indoors and outdoors. We offer a range of installation options and accessories to facilitate the process for you. You can head over to our PVC signs installation page to find detailed instructions on how to install your product.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Standoffs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Standoffs are silver or gold bolts that allow you to hang your PVC prints from a wall through holes drilled in the material. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>*Select the number of drilled holes and standoffs before placing your order to make installing your product easier. </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Easel backs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This mounting method is suitable for showcasing smaller sizes. You can place the display on a table, countertop or any other flat surface by putting it on an easel back.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Command strips</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Command strips get attached to the back of your PVC signs and get hidden from sight. This will give your product a smooth and sleek appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Suction cup and hooks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Mount your display onto smooth surfaces such as glass by using a suction cup and hooks. Select the number of drilled holes needed to easily run the hooks through them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison of PVC Signs and Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer a number of products similar to PVC signs but made of different materials, each with their own benefits. We’ll compare some of these products in the table below. Keep in mind that the prices displayed are for standard options without any extra features.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Product</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>PVC Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/dibond-signs/\">Dibond Signs</a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/gatorboard-signs/\">Gator Board Signs</a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/paper-poster-printing/\">Paper Poster Printing</a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/wooden-signs/\">Wooden Signs</a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size Range</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<