t can feature graphics in any color. You can also select your preferred thickness option for your styrene sign from our menu.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Styrene Signs Printing Options</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Printing on styrene is available in single-sided and double-sided options. We offer a high resolution, full color print on styrene using state-of-the-art printers and genuine UV-cured inks.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Styrene Prints Shapes and Sizes</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Styrene sign printing is available in custom shapes and sizes ranging from 4&rdquo;x4&rdquo; to 48&rdquo;x96&rdquo;. We offer standard, rounded, outline or overline cutting options. Choose the style that best suits your needs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are several ways to install these products, one of which is with the help of standoffs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>*Please note that you should select the drilled holes and standoff options from the design tool before finalizing your order.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison Chart of Styrene Signs and Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The chart below compares basic specifications for a styrene sign and similar products.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Styrene Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Foam Board Printing</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Gator Board Printing</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Corrugated Plastic Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size Range:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot;- 48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot;- 48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot;- 48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot;- 48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.02