oad/c_scale,dpr_auto,f_auto,q_auto:best,t_productPageHeroGalleryTransformation_v2,w_auto/india%20lob/posters/in_posters_002','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRmBFUO2hi8IXag84hJPzNNpRpOtE0sKfWfCw&s','inches',NULL,'<h2><strong>Paper Poster Printing Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Paper poster prints are an affordable, time-tested means of displaying visuals and texts. They have a set of features that’ll play to your advantage.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>High print quality</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Low cost</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Easy installation </strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Long-term indoor use</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Paper posters are your go-to option for a range of purposes, which is why they’re the most in-demand type of posters. Hang them on different surfaces like walls, windows, doors and beyond.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Paper Wall Posters </strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Paper wall posters are made of durable paper that shows off images and texts in high quality. They have a visual appeal that passers-by will appreciate. This medium is much more lightweight, affordable than other wall decor items such as <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-signs/\">acrylic signs</a>. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/ppp-1.jpg\" style=\"height:200px; width:400px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Decorative Paper Poster Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Create exceptional art displays with paper poster prints. Art paper posters are a more affordable alternative to other decorative solutions like <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-photo-prints/\">acrylic photo prints</a>. They’ll keep you satisfied with their vivid colors and excellent print quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Informational Paper Poster Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Use paper posters as a professional-looking and budget-friendly option if you’re aiming to communicate information. Order them in bulk to spread the word in an effective and fast way.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Promotional Paper Poster Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Paper poster printing is a popular medium to promote seasonal offers or new products. Design it with product images and descriptions. Add your logo for a boosted effect.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Other Applications of Paper Poster Prints</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This medium has more uses besides paper wall posters. Read on and find inspiration to harness the full potential of paper poster printing. </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Window Paper Posters </strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This product will turn heads when you place it on your windows or storefront. Promote your business or display working hours. In fact, provide any type of relevant information with small and large paper posters. </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Door Paper Posters</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you need to display when your store will be open and closed during the holidays? Get paper poster printing with all the information. Design it and display it on your door. You can put it up and take it down with no trouble.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Construction Area Paper Posters</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It’s vital to mark dangerous areas or display building permit information in construction sites. This material is optimized for indoor use, so we recommend that you place them outside for a short time and only in fine weather conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Announcement Board Paper Posters</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you want to announce an event, maintenance works or anything else? Get paper poster printing and place it on a board. Add visual content and bold headlines to make the design even more eye-catching.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Photo Paper Poster Material</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The base material we use for paper poster printing is a white paper poster. Its features will show you the advantages of this product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Get a photorealistic effect with photo paper poster material. Use it for advertisements, informative displays and decorative pieces. It’s 7 mils thick and lightweight. You can attach the products to any smooth surface. They’re an excellent medium that’ll grab the attention of passers-by. This material comes with a matte finish. In case you are looking for a thicker, more durable material, <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/gatorboard-signs/\">gator board printing</a> is a great option.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Shape and Sizes of Paper Poster Prints</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer this product in square and rectangular shapes. Determine the shape by setting the width and height. The corners are at 90° angles and pointed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The size ranges from 4”x4” to 58”x1740\". You can choose any size in this range but the common sizes are 11”x17”, 18”x24”, 24”x36” and 27”x40”. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/ppp-2.jpg\" style=\"height:200px; width:400px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Paper Poster Design and Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Use our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\">design tool</a> for your project. Our paper poster maker has all the features you need. This includes designer-made <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">templates</a> you can customize. You can also start from scratch and use our elements, text fonts, backgrounds and other features. If you have something else in mind, upload a ready-made design or image in several formats.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use state-of-the-art machinery and UV inks for your small and large paper poster projects. The print will have premium quality no matter how many items you order.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison of Paper Poster Prints and Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Compare the products below and find the best fit for your needs. Please keep in mind that the prices shown in the table are for the default options of each product.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td> </td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Paper Post