 and pull away from the wall to detach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong>&nbsp;Pull the tab of the adhesive strips off the wall until they come off.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Installation With Suction Cup &amp; Hook</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The suction cup and hook is an ideal option to hang your display from glass or other smooth surfaces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:&nbsp;</strong>Choose a clean, dust-free and smooth surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:&nbsp;</strong>Stick the suction cups by pressing them to the application area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:&nbsp;</strong>Pass the hooks through the pre-drilled holes on your display.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Installation With Zip Ties</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ideal for a hanging installation of displays that have grommets. You can select them as an option from our design menu.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:&nbsp;</strong>Choose the number of zip ties according to the number of grommets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:&nbsp;</strong>Pass the zip ties through the grommets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:&nbsp;</strong>Attach the zip ties to the installation area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:&nbsp;</strong>Tighten all the zip ties for a firm grip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:&nbsp;</strong>Cut off all the extra ends of the zip ties for a clean look.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Styrene Posters</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>This product is ideal for business branding, restaurant menus and store promotions as well as trade show booth, office and home decor. Its bendable and durable features give it versatility for displays of different shapes and sizes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Digital printing with UV inks</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.020&quot;, 0.030&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<