r Stands</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Setting up a tension fabric banner stand is as simple as setting up <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/tabletop-retractable-banners/\">tabletop retractable banners</a>. Assemble the tubes of the aluminum hardware and slide the pillowcase-like material over it. Zip up the graphics tightly at the base of the fabric for a secure finish. Learn more in our fabric banner stand installation guide.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Sizes of Tension Fabric Stands</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our tension fabric stand product is available in two sizes. The smaller of the two measures 38”x91” and provides plenty of room for you to display ample information about your business or even run a promotion. To be on the safe side, keep your design within a margin of 31”x84”, and rest assured that it will cover the entire surface of your product. The larger product measures 50.5”x91” and offers you even more room to enhance your brand image. The design margin for this size covers an area of 43.5”x84”. You can see these areas and sizes visualized more clearly on our<a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\"> sign design tool</a>. You can also check out our unique <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">sign templates</a> to create stunning visuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison of Tension Fabric Stands and Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Product</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Tension Fabric Stands</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/retractable-banners/\"><strong>Retractable Banners</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/x-stand-banners/\"><strong>X-Stand Banners</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/vinyl-banners/\"><strong>Custom Vinyl Banners</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n