er the frame. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3. </strong>Use the bottom zipper to secure the fabric by pulling it taut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/tension-fabric-stand-set-up-process.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Tension Fabric Stands</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>8.8 oz</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>High resolution, full color printing with dye sublimation inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Price Range:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$254 - $309.28</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single-sided, double-sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>38\"x91\", </p>\r\n\r\n			<p>50.5\"x91\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (Indoors/</strong></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><strong>Outdoors):</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4+ years / NA</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',91.00,50.50,91.00,38.00,NULL,0,1,245.618269,0.260675,NULL),(28,'Tension Fabric Displays','Tension fabric displays are a novel asset for any major event or trade show. They’re tasteful, durable and easy-to-assemble.','https://www.314display.com/cdn/shop/products/8ftx8ft-Tension-fabric-Display_c6dd65ae-5d66-4c14-8dcb-315ef3fd4ec9_1024x1024.jpg?v=1681976340','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT4-Yh7loL89VAqwHAiuivXgW3ozEHX5B-tbA&s','https://s1-ecp.signs.com/4434/583x357/Tension-Fabric-Display-hero-14409.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTYN3fBLlps-u4pDX-U6TRIFUz7uR8gVySblQ&s','inches',5,'<h2><strong>Tension Fabric Displays Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Let 