th:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Affordable</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Portable\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/setup.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Effortless\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/effortless.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Effortless</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Applications for SEG Frame Displays</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>An SEG display offers diverse solutions across various settings, enhancing environments and creating remarkable promotional visuals for various purposes. Whether drawing in customers for your business, sharing artwork with enthusiasts or creating memorable events, SEG frame displays provide impactful visual appeal for all your needs. Here are some examples.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>SEG Fabric Displays in Retail</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Enhance your retail environment with SEG fabric displays. Promote products and special offers with vivid, seamless graphics that grab everyone’s attention and add a dynamic touch to your store. For additional solutions, explore our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/business-banners/\">business banners</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sd-2.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>SEG Display in Events</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>An SEG display will help you create stunning event environments or promote upcoming occasions. Their high-quality visuals and customizable designs ensure your event entices potential guests, whether enhancing its atmosphere or drawing future attention.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sd-3.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>SEG Display in Exhibitions</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>An SEG display guarantees that your works stand out from the crowd, whether it’s a trade show or an art exhibition. With stunning, high-resolution visuals and easy setup, this marketing item is ideal for showcasing products, artwork or brand messaging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sd-4.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Specifications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Stand\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/stand.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stand</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aluminum Frame</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Material\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/face-material.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Material</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit Fabric, Silicone Edges</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"uv printing\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/uv-printing.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UV printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Size\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/multiple-sizes.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3ft, 10ft, 20ft</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"installation\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/installation.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Installation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Freestanding</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>SEG Fabric Display Material and Printing</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sd-5.jpg\" style=\"height:189px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>An SEG display features excellent backlit fabric with a silicone edge sewn directly onto it. Unlike <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/vinyl-banners/\">vinyl banners</a>, SEG fabric frame displays offer lower light reflection, making them ideal for applications where glare reduction is important. The SEG frame is a lightweight aluminum stand, enabling quick assembly, portability and durability.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p>We employ UV-printing technology to cure designs directly onto the fabric, resulting in higher-quality prints without volume loss. We also offer double-sided SEG display options.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fabric-based products such as <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/fabric-banners/\">fabric banners</a> and <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/tension-fabric-displays/\">tension fabric displays</a> are particularly suitable for indoor spaces with ample lighting, compared to <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/retractable-banners/\">retractable banners</a> and <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/x-stand-banners/\">x-stand banners</a>, which are made of vinyl.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Sizes for SEG Frame Displays</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our SEG display comes in three sizes:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>3ft SEG Display:</p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Dimensions: 34.25”x79.5”</li>\r\n		<li>Weight: 13 lbs</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>10ft SEG Display:</p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Dimensions: 119”x89.5”</li>\r\n		<li>Weight: 38 lb</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>20ft SEG Display:</p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Dimensions: 237”x89.5”</li>\r\n		<li>Weight: 79 lbs</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>We also offer 10ft SEG backlit displays. An SEG lightbox can further enhance your display’s visibility and appeal by adding illumination to your visuals.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The SEG lightbox is perfect for creating an impressive atmosphere. It invites people’s attention, especially in dimly lit environments. As with our non-lit options, you can customize your SEG lightbox to be single-sided or double-sided. No matter your goal, an SEG lightbox ensures that your message will stand out with vivid, backlit designs. Explore the potential of an SEG lightbox and elevate your displays today.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Setting Up SEG Fabric Frame Displays</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>How to assemble an SEG display?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>* Start with the corners and tuck the silicone edge into the frame channel.</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Step 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ensure the stitching is fully inserted into the channel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sd-6.jpg