uminum signs aren&rsquo;t the perfect fit for your requirements, check the table above and find similar products that may suit you better.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Are brushed aluminum signs similar to standard aluminum?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>They are similar, but they still look different. Both traditional and brushed aluminum signs are made of the same material. The thing is that standard aluminum displays have a smooth surface with a white coating, whereas brushed metal signs have a unique brushed texture. Check out our&nbsp;brushed aluminum signs specifications page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How can I store my brushed aluminum sign?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Wrap your brushed metal signs in a soft towel and place them away from sharp items to prevent scratches and other damage.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Can I make holes in my brushed aluminum sign?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, you can. However, if you damage your brushed aluminum signs, we won&rsquo;t be able to replace or repair them. If you don&rsquo;t want to risk damaging your sign, we can drill the holes for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What installation options do you offer for brushed aluminum signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer a range of installation methods for wall-mounted, dead-fixed and free-standing brushed metal signs. To learn more, visit our&nbsp;brushed aluminum signs installation page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How can I care for my brushed aluminum sign?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Gently rub your brushed aluminum sign with a soft damp towel. Repeat this action regularly to keep the display smooth and clean. Avoid using acidic liquids as they will damage the brushed aluminum sign.</p>','<h1><strong>Installation of Brushed Aluminum Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>There are multiple installation accessories for displaying brushed aluminum signs. You can choose the one that best matches your requirements. Brushed aluminum plaques can be installed with the following accessories: standoffs, easel backs, hanging clips, zip ties and command strips.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Standoffs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Required tools</strong>: Standoffs, a drill, screws, anchors, marker and measuring tape</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Standoffs include an anchor, screw, barrel, and a cap with a threaded stud. The anchor is used to fix the standoff to the wall. The standoff barrel is what spaces the sign at a desired distance from the wall. Then, the threaded stud is used to sandwich the sign with the cap which adds a decorative finish to the wall-mounted sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Preparation:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before the installation, take the measuring tape and find the perfect position for the installation. Take the sign with pre-drilled holes and place it on the wall. Using the holes on the sign as a guide, mark the areas of the standoffs on the wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong>: Drill 4 holes in the marked areas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong>: Install the anchors, leaving enough external threading to allow the barrel to attach to the exposed end.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong>: Now, take the barrel and screw it to the wall via the anchor. Repeat the same action with the rest of the barrels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4</strong>: Next, take the sign and line up the holes with the standoffs on the wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5</strong>: Take the caps with the threaded studs and fasten the sign on the standoffs. This will sandwich the sign between the barrel and the cap.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We&rsquo;re done. The sign is now securely mounted to the wall with standoffs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Command Strips</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Required tools</strong>: 4 pairs of command strips, masking tape, scissors, measuring tape</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Command strips will arrive in pairs already attached to the back of the sign. The strips consist of two identical layers &lsquo;clicked&rsquo; together. One side of the strip is covered with an adhesive layer, the other with hooks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Preparation:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To attain maximum adhesion, the surface of the installation must be clean and dry. Before the installation, thoroughly clean the area of application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next, take the measuring device and find the perfect placement for the installation. Adjust the brushed metal sign to your desired position and mark the area of application with masking tape.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong>&nbsp;Take the sign with command strips already attached to it and peel off the liners of the strips.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong>&nbsp;Press the sign with the strips against the surface in the pre-marked location.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:&nbsp;</strong>Now, once the sign is attached to its place, you can remove the masking tape.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:&nbsp;</strong>To ensure the adhesive will hold, remove the sign from its bottom corners, pulling it up and away from the surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong>&nbsp;Now, press the strips onto the wall for a few seconds to ensure that they are secure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong>&nbsp;Wait about an hour before reattaching the frame, to make sure the strips are securely attached to the surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7:&nbsp;</strong>Align the strips on the frame with the strips on the wall.&nbsp; Press the sign onto the wall until each pair of strips click and seal into place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We&rsquo;re done. The rigid sign is now securely fixed in its place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In case you need to remove the sign, grab its bottom corners, then pull it up and away from the surface. Finally, remove the strips by pulling them downward.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zip Ties</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:&nbsp;</strong>First, you need to find the perfect location and a fitted object for the zip tie installation. Position the pre-drilled holes of the sign into place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:&nbsp;</strong>Take one zip tie and pass it through one of the drilled holes on the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Now, thread the zip tie through the hole and around the object to be secured on. Pull the zip tie to tighten it around the sign and the object.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:&nbsp;</strong>Take the scissors and cut the extra end of the zip tie for a cleaner look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong>&nbsp;Repeat the same action with the rest of the applicable corners of the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We&rsquo;re done. The sign is now securely fixed into place from two or four corners as needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easel Backs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easel backs are lightweight cardboard stands to display small brushed aluminum signs on flat surfaces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong>&nbsp;Take the easel back and fold the wing inward to cut open the pre-dotted area. Repeat the same action with the other easel back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong>: Fold down the circular easel stabilizer and secure easel wings in the slot on both easel backs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong>: Peel off the tapes from the adhesive bands on both easel backs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong>&nbsp;Position the adhesive parts of the easel backs on both sides of the sign and press for a few seconds to make sure they are securely fixed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That&#39;s it. Now you are ready to display your small brushed aluminum&nbsp;sign on any flat surface.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications Of Brushed Aluminum Signs</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.032&rdquo;,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>0.125&rdquo;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standoffs, command strips, zip ties, easel backs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.556 lbs/ft2,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>0.765 lbs/ft2</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single and double-sided, full-color UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size Rage:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&rdquo;x4&rdquo; - 48&rdquo;x96&rdquo;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square/rectangle, rounded, overline or outline</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12&rdquo;x24&rdquo;, 18&rdquo;x36&rdquo;, 24&rdquo;x36&rsquo;&rsquo;, custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Usage (Outdoors/Indoors):</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+/10+ years with proper care</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',96.00,48.00,4.00,4.00,NULL,0,0,98.168868,0.440516,NULL),(31,'Sandwich Board Signs','Can\'t-miss addition for any business to attract customers! Set up and relocate easily. Change the graphics as often as needed!','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61qYwRO6wXL.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTjz2ey5NVr_zMiiibGxWOP1K_WPemflSNfHA&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQO7W0L8rEnQDq0sGB4CeiRvYz8M8BFv-sshA&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS79ms6MNbDi53YH-PkQwj2WSO1pyM83VGdLg&s','inches',6,'<h2><strong>Sandwich Board Signs Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom sandwich board signs are an old-school, effective means of advertising that’s still popular to this day. This doesn’t mean that they’re limited to advertising though, since our custom signs can serve several other purposes in various industries. Organizations and individuals alike use affordable, highly visible sandwich board signs to show off all kinds of graphics. Our sandwich sign displays come with numerous features that’ll play to your advantage:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Changeable graphics</li>\r\n	<li>Portable</li>\r\n	<li>Ballasting columns</li>\r\n	<li>Double-sided display</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">Brand Experts</a> offers various indoor and outdoor sandwich board signs.We ship anywhere in the UAE , offering free ground shipping for orders over $85 and under 36\" within the contiguous UAE. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>With A-frame structures, custom sandwich board signs are a sturdier alternative to other outdoor media like <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/25\">X-stand banners</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Sandwich Sign Types</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You’re free to choose whichever type of our portable sandwich board signs you want. They have the same display size but vary in other features. Read on to figure out the differences between them before placing an order.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sbs-1.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Standard Sandwich Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our regular sandwich sign option consists of white and black plastic. When you opt for this type, the image is printed on vinyl material that’s stuck to the frame after printing. You’re free to switch designs whenever you desire by peeling off the vinyl face and replacing it with the new one. The black or white sandwich board sign as a whole measures 26”x46”. The graphics displayed on it however, are 24”x36”. This option weighs 18.5 lbs. These frames have empty columns within them which can be filled with sand to make them more stable. This will add around 10 lbs to its overall weight. The frame has locking hinges to prevent the product from opening wider than intended.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Quick Change Sandwich Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We have quick-change sandwich sign stands in two colors: white and black. The designs are printed on a corrugated plastic material and inserted into the frames. The latter have so-called “stay tabs” that don’t allow the rigid material to fall off. As the name implies, this option allows you to change displays in a matter of seconds by pulling the old ones out of place and sliding new graphics in. Quick-change sandwich board signs measure 27”x47”. The size of the printed surfaces is 24”x36”. These products weigh 20 lbs and have ballasting columns which can hold about 10 lbs of sand. The locked hinges prevent the frame from opening more than it’s supposed to.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Sandwich Board Sign Replaceable Inserts and Displays</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sbs-2.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>A main advantage of sandwich board signs is they allow you to change the displays while keeping the structure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For a standard sandwich sign, just order vinyl graphics then stick them to the sign surface. They won’t leave any residue after removal but you can’t reuse the same face once removed. You should order new faces that measure 24”x36”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Premium quick-change sidewalk sandwich board signs further facilitate changing the inserts. Purchase <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/7\">PVC signs</a> or inserts made of other materials to replace them. Make sure the board you choose is 3/16\" thick or thinner. The size should be 24”x36”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whenever you purchase two or more pieces of the same product, you become eligible for special discounts!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Usage Of Sandwich Board Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Indoor and outdoor sandwich board signs serve a number of purposes. Print any custom design with us and get anything from retail sandwich board signs to informative displays. Read on to see what our customers bought this product for down below and draw inspiration to make your own.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/02/28/uses-of-sandwich-board-signs.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sbs-3.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Retail Sandwich Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Sandwich board advertising signs are commonly placed to promote special sales and provide information. Retail sandwich board signs may also be positioned to indicate working hours or open/closed information. With easily replaceable graphics, these products last for a long period of time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Real Estate Sandwich Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Alternatives to <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/36\">yard signs</a>, real estate sandwich board signs provide you with stability and reusability for your realtor business displays. They’ll give you visibility from both directions and boost the effectiveness of your display. Our custom outdoor sandwich board signs are waterproof and heavy enough to withstand gusts of wind.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Restaurant Sandwich Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Display your menu or the day’s special with customizable restaurant sandwich board signs. Get multiple graphics or inserts printed to effectively reuse your displays on a daily basis. Placed on the pavement outside your venue, your outdoor sandwich board signs will surely captivate prospective customers with mouth-watering designs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Sandwich Board Parking Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Use sandwich board parking signs outside your home or your establishment. Make sure to place them on level ground. Take the fold-up sign with you and reuse it day in and day out. These sandwich board parking signs are used for events, to designate parking spots and beyond.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Wedding Sandwich Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Put up wedding sandwich board signs to welcome guests or as a timeline. Print graphics that will ensure an aesthetically pleasing appearance. If you own an event planning company, make the most of this medium as an awesome addition to any wedding reception.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Church Sandwich Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Looking for directional or welcoming church posters? Sandwich signs are an effective, affordable option. You’re free to get any image or text printed on the surface and display it in or outside the church. The plastic is robust, so opt for and get changeable displays to reuse the structure over a long time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Material for Indoor and Outdoor Sandwich Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Plastic sandwich board signs require little maintenance apart from cleaning with a damp cloth. Since these products are waterproof, feel free to set them outdoors with your mind at ease.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The sheet of the graphics on the standard option is an adhesive vinyl material. Peel it off and replace it to reuse the construction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The inserts for the changeable sandwich board signs are corrugated plastic. You can later replace them with any rigid material with a thickness of 3/16” or less. Check our products to figure out which replacement inserts suit you best and make sure you buy them in 24”x36” dimensions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Sandwich Board Sign Design</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/02/28/sandwich-board-sign-design.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sbs-4.jpg\" style=\"height:223px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make your own sandwich board signs with our intuitive design tool․ Make breathtaking designs from scratch using our elements, backgrounds, and texts. If that’s not what you have in mind, you always have the option to upload your own image or benefit from our ready-made designs which are all available for free.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You should also specify what frame you need and choose a lamination option before placing an order.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Sandwich Board Sign Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We utilize UV inks to print sandwich sign images on adhesives and rigid inserts. The graphics won’t fade over time, not even under direct sunlight. The printed surface becomes matte while the unprinted sections retain the material’s initial look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bring your design to life through our online tool. Unleash your creativity with numerous templates and design elements at your disposal. By default, both displays will be printed with the same design. To order boards that have different images on either face or a board with only one side printed, you’ll need to contact our customer support team. Also consider ordering blank dry erase sandwich board signs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Sandwich Board Sign Lamination</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer lamination for this product to guarantee extra protection and functionality. Lamination is applied to the printable material, regardless if it’s the adhesive or insert type. The chassis won’t be laminated in any case.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/02/28/finish-types-of-sandwich-boards.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sbs-5.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Dry Erase Lamination</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Dry erase sandwich board signs are in high demand as they multiply the benefits. First, they serve protective purposes, like all lam options. Second, while you can get the board printed, you can also use the surface to write with a temporary marker. Erase the writing with a damp cloth or a mixture of alcohol and water. Don’t use abrasive cleaners as they may damage the surface. This option will make the surface glossy.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Glossy Lamination</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Laminate your display to protect it and provide it with extra glossiness. This option will give you the same appearance as the dry-erase option, but you won’t be able to erase the surface in case you use a temporary marker on it.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Matte Lamination</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Give your boards a glare-free appearance and protect them from damage with this option. The printing process already makes the surface matte so you’ll need to laminate it to make the unprinted parts of the display matte as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison of Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Take a look at the table below and check out similar products. Keep in mind that the prices listed are for the default options of respective products. Additional features may increase or decrease the price.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td> </td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Sandwich Boards</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Step and Repeat Banners</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Retractable Banners</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Pop-Up Displays</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>24”x36”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>96\"x96\", 120\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>33\"x78\", 45”x78”, 57\"x78”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>96”x96”, 120”x96”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Price </strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$157.99</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$311.93, $375.49</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$121.84, $169.1, </p>\r\n\r\n			<p>$244.48</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$785.93, $871.49</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>3.125” (closed)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.03\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.02\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.03\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><st