to pole banners</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/mesh-banners/\">Mesh Banners</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/mesh-banners/\">12”x12”-115”x1,680”</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-3.jpg\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/mesh-banners/\">This product has tiny holes that let air flow through, making these exterior banners ideal for windy weather. These outdoor banners are visible from a distance and maintain image quality for years.</a></u></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/fabric-banners/\">Fabric Banners</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/fabric-banners/\">12”x12”-115”x1,680”</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-4.jpg\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/fabric-banners/\">These items have triple-layered woven fabric that is resistant to wrinkling and reflect minimal light. The feature ensures excellent printing quality and opacity for these exterior banners.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Specifications of Outdoor Banners</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Types\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/types.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Types</p>\r\n\r\n<p>vinyl/mesh/fabric</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/light-weight.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.5-13 oz/yd2</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Printing\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/uv-printing-516951.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UV printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Lifespan\" src=\"https://cdn.squaresigns.com/images/media/lifespan.svg\" style=\"height:100px; width:100px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lifespan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2-5 years</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Printing of Exterior Banners</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-5.jpg\" style=\"height:189px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our UV-curing printers create high-quality visuals, ensuring vibrant images that last. Proper cleaning and care can extend the lifespan of exterior banners up to five years, similar to <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/business-banners/\">business banners</a> and <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/retractable-banners/\">retractable banners.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Material of Outdoor Banners</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-6.jpg\" style=\"height:189px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let’s take a look at the material for the different types of custom outdoor banners.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Exterior banners made of vinyl consist of a soft, 13 mil-thick PVC layer adept at showcasing large visuals despite their lightweight and slim design.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The second type consists of a 70%-30% vinyl-mesh blend. These <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/category/custom-banners/\">custom banners</a> are dotted with small holes that allow air to flow through.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The third type is a soft, 100% polyester material. Produced with closely woven threads minimizing light reflection, these exterior banners offer versatility for a set of applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Setup Of Custom Outdoor Banners</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Setting up custom outdoor banners is a breeze, especially with grommets. You have plenty of installation choices such as bungee cords, hanging clips and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How To Set Up Custom Outdoor Banners With Zip Ties?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>*Position the banner on the installation area.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/0b-7.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 1</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Pass the zip ties through the banner and the installation area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-8.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 2</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Tighten all the zip ties for a firm grip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-9.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 3</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Cut off all the extra ends of the zip ties for a clean look.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How To Set Up Exterior Banners With Pole Pockets?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also choose other setup options, like bungee cords, hanging clips and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-10.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Step 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Open the pole pockets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-11.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Step 2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Insert the pole through the pockets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-12.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Step 3</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Secure the poles in place at the installation spot.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Outdoor Banners FAQ</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Are Outdoor Banners Weatherproof?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our custom outdoor banners are weatherproof, designed to withstand rain, wind and sunlight. Although they are durable, extended exposure to extreme weather conditions may cause some wear and tear, similar to <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/step-and-repeat-banners/\">step and repeat banners</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How To Clean and Maintain Outdoor Banners?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To clean and maintain your outdoor banners, mix a mild detergent with water and gently scrub the surface. Store custom outdoor banners in a dry place and avoid folding if possible. During installation, secure the outdoor banners tightly to prevent flapping in the wind.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Are Outdoor Banners Fade-Resistant?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Absolutely! Our exterior banners are fade-resistant, ensuring they maintain their vibrant colors even with prolonged exposure to sunlight. Explore our high-quality products, including <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/x-stand-banners/\">x-stand banners</a>, available for direct delivery across the US and Canada.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Templates</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">All Templates</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-13.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Woman in a Spa Purple Beauty Salon Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-14.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Red and Black Informative Low Price Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-15.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lawn and Landscape With Lawn Mower Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-17.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yellow For Lease Notice With Text Property Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-18.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Grocery Market With Items on Sale Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-19.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hotel and Spa We\'re Open Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-20.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Two Whole Pizzas on a Pizzeria Open Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-21.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wellness Center Business Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-23.png\" style=\"height:150px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dog Wellness and Grooming Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/ob-24.png\" style=\"height:2