un your fingers along the perimeter of the frame to push the silicone edges in securely.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sf-8.jpg\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>SEG Banners FAQ</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>What Is An SEG Fabric?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>SEG fabric is a fine polyester material that presents your message elegantly. These fabric graphics feature a silicone edge that fits snugly into the aluminum frames.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Can I Wash And Dry The SEG Fabric?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, fabric graphics are washable. We recommend that you use a mild detergent and cold water for thorough cleaning. Don’t use harsh chemicals or bleach. SEG printing can be air-dried or tumble-dried in a low-heat setting.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Can I order an SEG fabric for my existing frame?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, SEG fabric printing can be customized to fit existing frames. Ensure that the size of your replacement SEG printing corresponds to the size of your frame.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What are the benefits of an SEG fabric?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Fabric graphics are easy to set up, transport and guarantee longevity indoors. It\'s effective for advertising your brand with style while cutting costs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Templates</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">All Templates</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sf-9.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobile Pet Dog and Cat Clinic Veterinary Services Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sf-10.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Logistics Truck With Cargo Ship and Containers Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sf-11.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>University Registration Open Student Photo Sign Template</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/sf-12.png\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\"