o put up a lawn sign?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide H or spider stakes for yard sign mounting. Check our installation page for detailed steps. Alternatively, you can install your custom yard sign using zip ties if the product includes grommets.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Are there any accessories for installing lawn signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides the choice of stakes for the product, the accessories we offer in our menu are grommets and zip ties.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Why are grommets used for yard signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Grommets come in handy for hanging yard signs from a fence. You can go to our tool and get grommets pre-spaced at 1” on each corner of the display.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How much are yard signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The pricing for custom lawn signs varies depending on several factors such as size and accessories. You can refer to the calculator at the top of the product page to check the pricing based on the measurements and quantity. Once you modify the features including the cutting options or accessories, the prices for custom yard signs will change correspondingly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What is the size of a personalized yard sign?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom yard signs range from 4”x4” to 48”x96” in size. The most commonly ordered size for a personalized yard sign is 24”x18”. Keep in mind that when you order these products in sizes greater than 48”x48”, the corrugated flutes will be horizontal and the product will no longer be compatible with stakes.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Where to get yard signs made?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you looking for unique yard sign solutions? We’re a professional sign-making company with years of expertise. Contact us now and design your yard sign in custom shapes and colors.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Do you provide shipping for a lawn sign?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, we ship yard signs across the uAE. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Do you offer discounts for custom yard signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Order a large number of custom yard signs and you’ll receive discounted rates for your products. Our discounts increase with the quantity of products you order.</p>','<h1><strong>Installation of Yard Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>In case of an H or spider stake, check the firmness of your yard’s soil. Do not use a hammer or other instrument for the mounting as the poles should easily press into soft dirt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Installation With H-stakes </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H-stakes work well in windy weather as they stay firmly rooted in the ground. The corrugated plastic is lightweight but durable enough to withstand outdoor conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Insert the bottom of the stake into the ground.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Thread the two wires through the corrugated flutes of the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Ensure your product is straight and securely installed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Installation With Spider Stakes</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check for soil consistency that’s firm but not too hard or brittle to ensure a sturdy anchor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Choose a level application area on the ground and insert the stake.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Slide the corrugated plastic onto the stake.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Ensure your display is straight and securely installed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Installation With Zip Ties:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We recommend getting your sign with pre-spaced grommets by selecting them from our accessories option in the design menu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Make sure that your product is level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Pass the zip tie through the grommet (pre-drilled hole).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Pull the zip tie tight until there is no wiggle room.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>Cut the extra part for a cleaner look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5: </strong>Repeat the process for as many zip ties as there are.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Yard Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.16\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Hanging, ground</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.22 lbs/sq ft</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation Accessories:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Grommets, zip ties</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Materials:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Coroplast</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>H Stake:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Small - 0.15\"Tx10\"Wx15\"H</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Big - 0.15\"Tx10\"Wx30\"H</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12\"x6\", 24”x12”, 24\"x18\", 24\"x24\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Spider Stake:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.6\"Tx8\"Wx26\"H</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min. Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Method:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Digital printing with fade-resistant UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max. Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>96”x48</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single-sided, double-sided </p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>White</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square, rectangle, circle, oval, overline, outline</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Construction:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>H-stake, spider stake metal frame</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+ years with proper care</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>',48.00,96.00,4.00,4.00,NULL,0,0,45.950013,0.121212,NULL),(37,'Corrugated Plastic Signs','An affordable option that serves a range of promotional and informative purposes. The product is weather-resistant and suitable for indoor and outdoor use.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRglBhpnNz_Mc2aY9PIGjpqwZWQoYE3toi6RQ&s','https://pyramidprintingok.com/cdn/shop/files/Yard_Signs_Real_Estate_Marketing_A.jpg?v=1682624278','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSyfPzNtTiHuXb_E5jiKQbtEy4KGht9xugEyQ&s','https://s.alicdn.com/@sc04/kf/He2aeab17cc2e43eeaf997ed3506adae6M.jpg_300x300.jpg','inches',1,'<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Corrugated Plastic Signs Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Looking for unique and durable <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/custom-signs/\">custom signs</a> to get your message across indoors and outdoors? Corrugated plastic signs are a cost-effective solution ideal for promotional and informative use.  </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Corrugated signs are 0.16” thick plastic panels made of coroplast. They’re water-proof and resistant to most weather conditions so with proper maintenance, they’ll serve you for a long time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"www.brandexperts.ae\">brandexperts</a> offers single and double-sided printing options for corrugated plastic signs. The double-sided printing can be freestanding or hanging to ensure two-way visibility and amplify your message. Coroplast signs are portable and almost as lightweight as <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/pvc-signs/\">PVC signs</a>. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Shapes for Corrugated Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer the following three cutting options for our corrugated signs: </p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Square / Rectangle Cut - cut with 90 degree edges</li>\r\n	<li>Outline Cut - cut in the exact shape of your design</li>\r\n	<li>Overline Cut - cut in the shape of your design with a white border</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Popular Applications for Coroplast Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/15/cps-1.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coroplast signs are a multipurpose medium used to attract the attention of passersby, be they on foot or in vehicles. They’re versatile with a wide range of applications. The most common uses for these plastic signs include but are not limited to: </p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Promotional signs - These signs, similar to <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/yard-signs/\">yard signs</a>, are popular for displaying promotional messages. They capture the attention of passersby and reach a wide audience with vibrant graphics.</li>\r\n	<li>Informative signs - They can also be used to share any kind of information. Just like <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/aluminum-signs/\">aluminum signs</a>, they’re a great medium for relaying instructions, business hours, directions and so on.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: Avoid folding your corrugated signs when storing to prevent damage.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Corrugated Plastic Signs FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What installation options are available?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer several installation options with H and spider stakes, command strips, grommets and zip ties. Check out our installation section for detailed instructions. Keep in mind that when you order these products in sizes greater than 48”x48”, the corrugated flutes will be horizontal and the product will no longer be compatible with stakes.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What’s the lifespan of coroplast signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Under moderate conditions, these displays will serve outdoors for more than 3 years.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Can corrugated plastic signs withstand heat?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Corrugated plastic signs can withstand heat as well as snow, hail, heavy rain and freezing temperatures</p>','<h1><strong>Installation Options for Corrugated Plastic Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer five different accessories for the installation of this product. It can be mounted on stakes or hung using zip ties, grommets and command strips.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Installation With H-Stakes:</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>H-stake signs are ideal for windy weather as they get firmly rooted in the ground. Choose an area with soft dirt to insert the stake without the need for additional tools.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Mark the place on the ground where you want to position the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Draw the two wires through the corrugated flutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Fix the bottom of the sign into the ground.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Installation With Spider Stakes:</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Check the firmness of the soil and choose ground that’s not too hard or too brittle. The poles should easily press into soft dirt without the need for any additional tools.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Find a flat surface for the stake installation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Carefully slide the sign onto the stake.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Push the bottom of the spider stake into the soil.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Installation With Grommets:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer grommets for hanging installation. We’ll fix the grommets onto the corners of the sign to streamline the process for you. You can insert zip ties, bungees, nylon ropes, hanging clips or any other hardware you prefer through the grommet holes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Take your sign with the pre-fixed grommets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Pass the hanging hardware of your choice through each grommet hole.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Pass the hardware through the target location. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Fix it firmly into place per hardware requirements. </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Installation With Zip Ties:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You may also use zip ties to hang up your corrugated displays. Choose the grommet option for a clean look or pierce holes into the sign as you see fit. Make sure to leave enough space around the edges to prevent the material from ripping or cracking. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Make sure that the application surface is level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Pass the zip ties through the holes on the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Fasten the sign to the target location.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>Secure the zip ties. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Cut the extra parts of the ties for a neater look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Installation With Command Strips:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This is the best accessory for hanging your sign from the wall without any visible installation hardware.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Clean the surface before attaching the sign to it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Peel off the strip backing from one side to adhere it to the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Make sure the strips are firmly attached to the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4</strong>: Peel off the protective backing to apply the sign to the wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Detach the sign from the wall by holding it from the bottom corners.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Wait for at least an hour for the command strips to adhere to the wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7:</strong> Apply the sign back to the wall by reattaching the strips</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications for Corrugated Plastic Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.16”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Options</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single or double-sided printing</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Materials</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Coroplast</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting Options</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, overline or outline</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min Size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation Accessories</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Grommets, zip ties, command strips</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max Size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>48\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>H Stake</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Small - 0.15\"Tx10\"Wx15\"H, Big - 0.15\"Tx10\"Wx30\"H</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12\"x6\", 24\"x18\", 24\"x24\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Spider Stake</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.6\"Tx8\"Wx26\"H</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>White</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (Indoors/Outdoors)</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+ / 3+ years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',48.00,96.00,4.00,4.00,NULL,0,0,22.556188,0.121212,NULL),(38,'Real Estate Signs','Lightweight, budget-friendly and easy-to-use realtor signs will promote your house listings with style, be it rain or shine.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSL8YSBDKqVIKgb8f7qU11KLPj77FNGrieZqQ&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSrqm0xIgFfNffqH3SVTyAPdcMbkJfKjXAEAQ&s','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71DyrUDoSIL.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS7hROkPdoCSZp2ShCnpiUElnP9yHag8UO86A&s','inches',1,'<h2><strong>Real Estate Signs Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Real estate signs are an in-demand subcategory of <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/yard-signs/\">yard signs</a>. These budget-friendly and lightweight marketing tools are placed on the lawn to get the word out about property listings. Our realtor signs are composed of fluted plastic displays and simple installation stakes. These are the top features of our custom real estate signs:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Resilient materials</li>\r\n	<li>UV-protected graphics</li>\r\n	<li>Creative shapes</li>\r\n	<li>Easy installation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Get <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/for-lease-signs/\">For Lease Signs</a> with engaging texts and graphics if you’re planning to put properties up on the market. You can pair them with <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/open-house-signs/\">Open House Signs</a> to reach your audience and invite them in for a viewing. These products are affordable marketing solutions suitable for temporary lawn promotions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Create and order real estate signs with Square Signs and get them shipped anywhere within the US and Canada. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Popular Realtor Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Promote your announcements and pique your audience’s curiosity through popular realtor signs. These commercial grade <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/corrugated-plastic-signs/\">corrugated plastic signs</a> serve as handy, lightweight tools to promote your properties. Find the type of product that best suits your needs below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Real Estate For Sale Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/rs-1.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you want to sell your house or apartment but find it challenging to attract customers? Order real estate for sale signs with creative design solutions. Get your real estate for sale sign cut into a unique shape and set it up in your yard. Along with captivating texts and images, they’ll catch the eye of any prospects passing by and lead them straight to you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Sold Real Estate Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/rs-2.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you’ve already closed on a property but still have customers contacting you, remove your real estate for sale sign and replace it with a sold real estate sign. You can come up with a unique design solution to differentiate it from a “for sale” lawn display. Customize your sold real estate sign using our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\">design tool</a> by selecting distinct colors, texts and icons.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Coming Soon Real Estate Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/rs-3.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Plan to sell your house soon and want to keep customers in the loop? Get a coming soon real estate sign announcing the upcoming sale. A coming soon real estate sign is a necessity if you wish to attract a large number of buyers. Set up your coming soon real estate sign on visible areas of the lawn or near the driveway and let it reel in clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Real Estate Agent Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/rs-4.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Realtor signs advertise property sales and promote the services of real estate agents. If you are a broker, promote your services with a classy real estate sign design. As a professional real estate sign maker, our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\">design platform</a> will help you personalize your product. Upload a photo and add contact information to maximize your product’s effectiveness. To preserve the appeal of realtor signs, choose colors like green and blue which are ideal for exuding professionalism and trust.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Custom Real Estate Signs Design</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Realtor signs, though mainly used for commercial purposes, can be transformed into decorative displays with an elegant finish and vibrant images. Use <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-signs/\">acrylic signs</a> to create the most exquisite hanging real estate signs. Take <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/aluminum-signs/\">aluminum signs</a> into consideration for the same end; they’ll give your realtor signs an unmatched look. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Go classy with a real estate sign design on <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/pvc-signs/\">PVC signs</a>. The material provides additional sturdiness and a more substantial look. The weather-proof properties and enhanced lifetime of this product will ensure your realtor sign serves its purpose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you want to show off listings with striking realtor signs or have a simple-looking display for one-time use? Either way, our intuitive and <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\">free design tool</a> can help you make it. Pick the best colors for your realtor sign, change the background, add icons and texts. Do you want to offer professional services? Upload your photo and add contact information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Browse our list of <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/real-estate/open-house/\">realtor sign templates</a> if you\'re short on ideas or if you’re searching for inspiration to make your own real estate sign. Choose your favorite, redesign it or use it as is.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Popular Sizes for Real Estate Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer real estate signs ranging between 4”x4” and 48”x96” in size. The price list below corresponds to standard realtor sign dimensions without extra options and accessories.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12”x18”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>18”x24”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>24”x24”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>24”x36”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>36”x48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Price</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$12.15</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$18.67</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$23.02</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$31.72</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$57.82</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>*The prices in this chart may be outdated. To check the current prices and discounts for this product, please refer to the calculator at the top of the page.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Main Features of Real Estate Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Did you decide to purchase realtor signs? Learn the product specifications and features. Find out if it can satisfy your expectations.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Real Estate Sign Printing and Materials</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/rs-5.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We manufacture realtor signs using a fluted polypropylene material displayed on installation stakes. We also offer other accessories you can order. The realtor sign material is water-proof, resistant to most weather changes and affordable for one-time use. Our real estate sign printing can be either single or double-sided with UV-protected graphics which prolong the lifespan of realtor signs, letting them serve more than three years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our custom real estate signs are available in the following cutting options:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Square / Rectangle </strong>- cut with 90° angles</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Outline </strong>- cut in the exact form of your graphics</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Overline </strong>- cut in the form of the design with a border around it</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Mounting Options for Real Estate Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our realtor signs are light but sturdy enough to set up and use under changing weather conditions. We have two hardware options you can use to put up your custom real estate sign. Find detailed instructions on our real estate signs installation page.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Mounting with stakes</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Our spider stakes and H-stakes are low-cost installation accessories for real estate signs. The former measures 0.6\"Tx8\"Wx26\"H while the latter comes in two sizes: 10”x15” and 10”x30”. Whichever you choose, your custom real estate sign will be secure with the mount rooted deep in the soil.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Keep in mind that when you order these products in sizes greater than 48”x48”, the corrugated flutes will be horizontal and the product will no longer be compatible with stakes.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Mounting with zip ties</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Another mounting option for real estate signs is with zip ties. They’re used to attach the displays to wire fences and other applicable surfaces. Order a realtor sign with preset grommets from our menu to run the zip ties through with a clean look. Even in windy conditions, your product wil