e case of installation with a ground stake, choose a level ground area and hammer the base deep into the soil.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Teardrop Flags</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Face Material:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Polyester flag material</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Dye sublimation</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 oz.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single-sided</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Reverse-sided</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Double-sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>White</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation Hardware:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 piece pole, 1 base, bungee cord, loop, metal ring</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Small (23.17”x63.52”)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Medium (32.54”x78.64”)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Large (40.38”x101.63”)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>X-Large (44.95”x140.75”)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Base Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Ground stake,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>square base,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>cross base,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>cross base + water bag</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Sizes with Hardware:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Small (7 ft.)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Medium (9 ft.)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Large (11.2 ft.)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>X-Large (13.5 ft.)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>2+ years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',140.75,44.95,63.52,23.17,NULL,0,1,376.516585,0.107914,NULL),(44,'Rectangle Flag Banners','Vibrant, durable and unique rectangle flags offer an innovative way to promote business promotions and share announcements.','https://i.etsystatic.com/30658943/r/il/652495/4238187198/il_570xN.4238187198_rpzz.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTOm7BNlrONa0H09jvu3wRI-i9EaQ8DyNE-TA&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSGr706U4Y_LgmjkeAym0YLX06xuF2Smiiajw&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRlUg-YlHnzno0Q8BCwgzW8QZSZqFS0Ao8R4g&s','inches',5,'<h2><strong>Rectangle Flag Banners Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Use custom rectangle flags to draw attention to your message. Durable materials make the construction suitable for moderate weather conditions. The unique rectangle banner design will ensure your design stands out from its surroundings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rectangle flag banners are popular marketing tools used for displaying promotional and informative content just like <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/73\">feather flags</a> and <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/43\">teardrop flags</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Design your rectangle flag banner on our website and place your order within minutes. Brand Experts will deliver your rectangle flag to any location across the UAE .<img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/rfb-1.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Rectangle Banners for Different Uses</strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/02/28/promotional-rectangle-flag.jpg\" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Similar to <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/44\">retractable banners</a>, our rectangle flags showcase advertisements that capture attention from a distance. Create an original rectangle banner with our free and intuitive sign design tools.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Rectangle Flags for Promotions</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Create a personalized custom rectangle flag with our ready-made design layouts and use it for trade exhibitions, seasonal sales and other occasions. Just like our <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/6\">vinyl banners</a>, rectangle flag banners show illustrations with bright and vibrant colors.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Rectangle Flags for Announcements</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Use the rectangle banner design anywhere you like to share announcements with your audience. These versatile flags are eye-catching and perfect for drawing attention.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Main Features of Rectangle Flags</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Explore all the characteristics of this product and place your order.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Material of Rectangle Banners</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Rectangle flag banners are composed of a polyester face and aluminum hardware. The components of the product are delivered in a package. Assemble your custom rectangle flag banner and slip the face over the construction to use it. Rectangle banners serve for a minimum of two years if you take good care of them.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Rectangle Flag Banners</strong> <strong>Printing Options</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/rfb-2.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We produce our custom rectangle flags with dye sublimation printing technology. The three printing options we offer for rectangle banners are listed below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Single-Sided Rectangle Banners</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>These visuals cover only one side of a rectangle banner but may be slightly visible from the other side if placed under direct light.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Reverse-Sided Rectangle Banners</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>This method uses single-sided printing but the image is mirror-printed so you can display two custom rectangle flags side-by-side.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Double-Sided Rectangle Banners</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>This technique applies imagery on both sides of a rectangle flag banner so you can gain double the exposure for your message