his chart may be outdated. To check the current prices and discounts for this product, please refer to the calculator at the top of the page.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Rectangle Flag</strong> <strong>FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to create a unique rectangle banner design?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our free design platform will let you create unique designs for your rectangle banner from scratch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Where do you ship rectangle banners?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>We deliver all our products to any location within the UAE.</p>','<h1><strong>Installation of Rectangle Flag Banners</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>You’ll receive the product packed in a standard box. It’ll take about 5 minutes to assemble the construction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Carefully remove all the pieces from the bag.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Connect the 2 long bottom rods using the push buttons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Take the third rod with a clamp and attach it to the other 2 rods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>Unscrew and remove the clamp to slide the face over the pole.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Slide the face over the pole set through the longer pole pocket.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Slide the shortest top pole through the short pocket of the face material.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7:</strong> Connect the long and short pole sets to each other.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 8:</strong> Attach the clamp back to the bottom of the pole and tighten it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 9:</strong> Attach the completed set to the base you’ve selected.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 10:</strong> Pull the bungee cord on the pole through the loop on the face.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 11: </strong>Tie and knot the bungee cord to secure the face to the pole.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> In the case of installation with a ground stake, choose a level ground area and hammer the base deep into the soil.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Rectangle Flag Banners</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Face Material:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Polyester flag material</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Style:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Dye sublimation</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 oz.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single-sided, reverse-sided, double-sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>White</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation Hardware:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 piece pole, 1 base, clamp, bungee cord, loop</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Small (31”x90.5”)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Medium (31”x114”)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Large (31”x151.5”)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Base Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Ground stake,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>square base,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>cross base,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>cross base + water bag</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Hardware Height:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Small (8.5 ft.)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Medium (11.8 ft.)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Large (15 ft.)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>2+ years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',151.50,31.00,90.50,31.00,NULL,0,1,391.324743,0.139248,NULL),(45,'Foam Board Signs','Get the best out of the two worlds a professional, catchy, sharp look combined with super light weight','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81ASR0b9QiL._AC_UL480_FMwebp_QL65_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/516wEE7dasL._AC_UL480_FMwebp_QL65_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51XRjqTMGwL._AC_UL480_FMwebp_QL65_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/3103JZmyJJL._AC_UL480_FMwebp_QL65_.jpg','inches',1,'<h2><strong>Foam Board Printing Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Foam board signs present a perfect solution for short to mid-term indoor use. They’re affordable and still provide a professional look. The banner is made of foam sandwiched between clay-coated paper faces. It’s safe to say that it’s light as a feather, but provides high durability. Foam board signs come with compelling features, some of which are listed below.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Excellent print quality</li>\r\n	<li>High durability</li>\r\n	<li>Light weight and smoothness</li>\r\n	<li>Cost-effectiveness</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">Brand Experts</a> offers custom foam board printing for all types of needs and occasions with shipping across the UAE. We even provide free ground shipping within the contiguous UAE for orders over $85 which are smaller than 36\" in size. Use our design tool to style your signage and create unique designs. Our customer support agents are ready to help you whenever you have any questions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Foam Board Signs by Usage</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/03/foam-board-signs.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>These custom signs have a wide array of applications from decorative to promotional. While our platform allows for designing fully personalized foam core signs, here are some of the most common uses to inspire you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Foam Board Photo Prints & Decor</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Photo prints on this material provide an affordable alternative to more expensive ones like acrylic signs or  metal photo prints. Plus, they’re much easier to mount because they’re so light. Foam board printing provides superior colors and resolution, so your decors will have a modern feel to them.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Foam Board Event Displays</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Foam prints are quite a good choice for event or exhibition displays since they’re so cost-effective. Get foam board printing with your logo and brand name to be showcased near your booth or table. Your brand will be the center of attention and you won’t pay a fortune for one-time usage.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Foam Board Promotional Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Promote your business indoors with printed boards. Showcase your seasonal promotions and grab the attention of prospects with dazzling displays. You have the options to mount them on the wall, set them on stands or even hang them from the ceiling. This product is so easy to use!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Foam Board Informational Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Want to highlight a safety notice or business hours? Custom foam board posters are effective tools for communicating information. Get foam board sign printing with the needed text and simply place it in a highly-visible location. Include icons and other visual elements for even greater exposure.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Foam Board Presentation Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Need signage to make presentations? You’re at the right place. Custom foam displays are weightless, meaning you’ll be able to carry them and place them anywhere. Use our platform to design your print with our sign templates or upload one of your own images to get the highest-quality foam board printing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Popular Foam Board Poster Sizes</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/fbp-2.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer foam board printing for posters ranging between 4”x4” and 48”x96” in size. Whether you need 24”x36” foam board printing or any other size between those extremes, here’s a list of the most popular sizes along with their prices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Keep in mind that the stated prices don’t include any extra options. They are for the default foam board printing options: square/rectangle shapes, single-sided printing, without drilled holes or accessories.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Standard Sizes</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>12\"x12\"</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>12”x24”</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>24”x24”</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>18\"x36\"</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>24”x36</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Price for 3/16\"</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$18.55</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$22.68</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$30.96</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$33.02</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$39.23</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Price for 1/2\"</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$31.35</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$41.02</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$60.36</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$65.19</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$79.69</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>*The prices in this chart may be outdated. To check the current prices and discounts for this product, please refer to the calculator at the top of the page.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Shape Options for Foam Board Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/fbp-3.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Create custom foam board posters in any shape you like by using our design platform. To guide you through the process of shaping your boards, here are the available options explained. Choose the one you like during the design process so we cut it the way you prefer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Square/Rectangle</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The standard shape of foam board signs comes with pointed 90° angles. It’s the most preferred shape for the paper-faced board for personal and business needs. This is the default foam board printing option in our tool and is free of charge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Rounded</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The rounded option has the same shape as the default square or rectangle cuts. Yet, the pointed corners are rounded at a ½”, ¾” or 1” ratio, depending on the size. This option will give your foam board printing a softer appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Outline</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you need a custom shape for your boards? Get them outline cut on our platform. All you need to do is create a design that has a distinct outline and choose the respective cutting option.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Overline</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Along with the same features that the outline cutting option has, overline cutting comes with an added ¼\"-½\" border around your design. The border will have the natural color of the material, which is white in this case. If you need the border to have another color or pattern, include it in the design and choose the outline option instead. Please keep in mind that the border size will be included in the overall product size you choose.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Foam Board Poster Printing and Material</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/fbp-4.jpg\" style=\"height:119px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The material of foam board signs is a foam sheet between two layers of paper. Those layers are firmly attached and won’t peel off. The product comes in two thickness options: 3/16” and 1/2”. While the first is sturdy enough for medium-sized foam board posters, the second is preferable for large displays.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The paper faces enhance the quality of foam board poster printing. We use UV-inks so your printed graphics will last longer even under direct sunlight.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Foam Board Printing on One Side</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>While both faces are printable, the default and widely used option is getting only one side printed. Single-sided foam core printing has its advantages. You get the product outline or overline cut, with no concerns about the design staying out of the mirrored shape on the reverse side.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Foam Board Printing on Both Sides</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to extract the best your foam board posters can offer, get both sides printed with the same or different designs. Double-sided foam board printing lets you achieve even greater exposure. Opt for a different design printed on each side to convey more information. If you have questions, please contact our support team.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Mounting Options for Foam Board Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Foam board posters come with a range of mounting options. Select the needed accessories on our design tool and order them along with your display. Please keep in mind that you’ll also need to select the number of drilled holes and their positioning if you want us to drill them for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Direct Mounting</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stick foam board posters directly to the wall or any other surface with command strips. This option doesn’t require drilled holes and it won’t leave any residue. The recommended way to apply this option is by placing strips on the four corners of your foam board poster. They can support up to 12 Ibs of weight, so rest assured that the product stays put.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Free Standing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The foam board isn’t self-supporting, but you can lean it against a wall or put it on a stand. We offer easel backs that work just like the easels of photo frames. They’re intended for relatively smaller foam prints. Read all the relevant information about the sizes of the easels and the products they can hold while choosing your accessories on our tool.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hanging</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since foam board signs are light you’re free to hang them on the wall or storefront window. If you’ve chosen foam board printing on both sides consider hanging them from the ceiling for maximum efficiency. Choose suction cups and hooks or zip ties from the accessories.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Comparison of Foam Board Signs with Similar Products</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Here’s a list of similar products to make your choice easier. Please note that the prices shown below are for the default options of each product you’ll find in our tool. Advanced features and accessories will add to these prices.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p> </p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Foam Board Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/gatorboard-signs/\"><strong>Gator Board Signs</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/pvc-signs/\"><strong>PVC Signs</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/styrene-signs/\"><strong>Styrene Signs</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-photo-prints/\"><strong>Acrylic Photo Prints</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size range</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\" - 48\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\" - 48\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\" - 48\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\" - 48\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\" - 48\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.188\", </p>\r\n\r\n			<p>0.5\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.188”,<br />\r\n			0.5”,<br />\r\n			1”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.125”,<br 