 other material-related deformations.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What’s the average lifespan of foam board printing products?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Foam board posters can withstand decades of constant usage. Please bear in mind that it’s intended for only indoor use because of the nature of the material.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Do you offer shipping?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, we ship products across the US and Canada. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts</p>','<h1><strong>Installation of Foam Board Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Foam board sign installation with command strips</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you feel the need, you can create a middle hinge for a level installation of your <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/foamboard-signs/\">foam board signs</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Once you get everything in position, stick the strip or the tape from the back side of the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Slightly press to make sure it is firmly adhered onto the surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Peel the second back tape off of the adhesive, stick to the marked location</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Foam board Sign installation with suction cup & hook</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Position the cup onto a glossy surface (glass, metal), assure it is level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Position the suction cups to all corners or necessary angles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Burp the air out by pressing the central part of the suction cup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Put the hook back to its place and, finally, hang the sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Foamboard sign installation with zip ties</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Wrap the zip tie around the application surface and the drilled holes with the locks looking outwards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Position the sign level and snap lock the zip ties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Cut the extra-long part for a more aesthetic look.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications of Foam Board Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thikness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.188\", </p>\r\n\r\n			<p>0.5\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Directly mounted onto the surface with suction cup & hook, double-sided tape or command strips or fixed with zip ties or easel backs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.15 lbs/ft²,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>1.07 lbs/ft²</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Digital - Direct printing with fade and sun resistant UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min. Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single sided, Double sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max. Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>48\"x96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, overline, outline, rounded</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12\"x12\", 12\"x24\", 18\"x36\", 24\"x24\", 24\"x36\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Drilled hole options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 corners, right and left center, top and bottom center, top corners only, 4 corners and top and bottom center</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>White</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>25+ indoors, not recommended for outdoor usage</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FAQs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What is a foam board sign?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Foam board is made of a polystyrene foam core sandwiched between two clay-coated papers. Foam board is lightweight, eco-friendly and affordable. The paper finish gives the foam board signs a matte finish and color vividness. No wonder they’re so popular for indoor decorations and signage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Where can I use a foam board sign?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Foam board is lightweight and affordable yet looks elegant and expensive. That’s why it has such wide usage in so many fields. Foam board is used for:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Indoor decorations</li>\r\n	<li>Company name and logo signs</li>\r\n	<li>Presentations</li>\r\n	<li>Trade show booths</li>\r\n	<li>Photograph print backs</li>\r\n	<li>Directional signs</li>\r\n	<li>Classroom posters</li>\r\n	<li>And much more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Foam board printing is available with an excellent matte finish that gives the sign a professional look. With proper care, these signs will last for many years indoors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What inks do you use for foam board printing?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For foam board printing, we use high quality UV inks. These inks provide color vividness and clarity on many materials including foam board. Foam board prints can serve as attractive signs, photo prints, poster boards and so on. What is more, you can have double sided printing on foam boards. This means more visibility and more information for passers-by. You can have the same message as well as different messages printed on each side. You can transfer any information on foam boards via printing; images (both personal and stock), texts, graphic designs. Foam board printing gives you all the opportunities.</p>',48.00,96.00,4.00,4.00,NULL,0,0,61.321281,0.122243,NULL),(46,'Gator Board Printing','Resistant To Bending And Denting - Gator Board Signs Are Suitable For Everything From Stylish Decor To Sophisticated Office Signage.','https://s1-ecp.signs.com/2799/Gatorboard-Shopping-3-01-9312.jpg','https://s1-ecp.signs.com/2799/Gatorboard-Shopping-3-01-9312.jpg','https://s1-ecp.signs.com/2799/Gatorboard-Shopping-3-01-9312.jpg','https://s1-ecp.signs.com/2799/Gatorboard-Shopping-3-01-9312.jpg','inches',NULL,'<h2><strong>Gator Board Printing&nbsp;Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom gator board signs are sturdy, lightweight media that serve an array of purposes. From &ldquo;open&rdquo; and &ldquo;closed&rdquo; door hangers to photo displays, they&rsquo;re an inexpensive option with a professional appearance. Gator board signs offer numerous advantages:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Light weight</li>\r\n	<li>High print quality</li>\r\n	<li>Two printing surfaces</li>\r\n	<li>Extended indoor lifespan</li>\r\n	<li>Easy installation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">Brand Experts</a>&nbsp;offers gator board printing in custom sizes, shapes and thicknesses with a selection of different accessories.&nbsp;We provide shipping all across the UAE. Order&nbsp;custom signs&nbsp;now and benefit from our free ground shipping within the contiguous US for orders over $85 and under 36&quot; in size.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Usage of Gator Board Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Also spelled as gatorboard, this product serves a multitude of purposes. You can sketch any kind of custom gator board signs you can envision, and just to get your creative juices flowing, these popular ideas may help you come up with some pretty unique and attractive designs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Different gator board signs for different purposes on white and black material\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/03/usage-of-gator-board-signs.jpg\" title=\"usage of gator board signs\" width=\"960\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Informative Displays</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you need &ldquo;open&rdquo; and &rdquo;closed&rdquo; hanging displays or safety notices, this medium is a great choice. It&rsquo;s as light as&nbsp;foam board printing&nbsp;with the added benefit of being more durable. It can withstand even rougher handling.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Advertising Gator Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Print promotional graphics on this medium to achieve a professional appearance which makes for effective advertising. With a wide range of mounting alternatives, you can set it up anywhere in any venue.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Decorative Boards</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Use this material to decorate your walls with quotes or create wedding boards if you want a more lightweight alternative to other mediums like&nbsp;custom acrylic signs. Its base coat comes in either black or white, but you can choose any other background color to be printed on it.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Gator Board Photo Prints</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>More affordable than&nbsp;acrylic photo prints, gator board photo printing provides top quality visuals. Whether you need them for home decor or as gallery exhibits, custom gator board signs will leave you satisfied.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Wayfinding Panels</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Create a better guest experience at your venue with a wayfinding system implemented through gator board printing. You can have them cut in the shape of arrows or any other custom shape you can think of.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Gator Board Printing and Material</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We use UV inks and state-of-the-art machinery to provide you with quality products. We have two alternatives for you to choose from for gator board printing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/03/gator-board-signs-printing-options.jpg\" width=\"960\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Single-Sided Gator Board Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Get gator board printing on one side of the material and showcase it on a wall, easel or elsewhere. Your message or graphics will get a lot of attention with this option.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Double-Sided Gator Board Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Make the most of your product with double-sided gator board printing. Hang it to showcase both of them or flip it to change the display whenever you need. By default, we print the same design on both sides. Contact us in case you want to have different designs printed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This material consists of a composite foam core coated with wood fiber veneer. The faces may look and feel like paper but they last longer. The material comes in all white (core and coating) or all black options.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You also have the following thickness choices: 3/16&quot; (0.188&quot;), 1/2&quot; (0.5&quot;) and 1&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Cutting Options for Custom Gator Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Style your display in the form you like with our different cutting options. Even though you can get any custom shape with us, we still offer some popular standard options for an even more personalized appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/03/gator-board-signs-shapes.jpg\" width=\"960\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Square/Rectangle Cut</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>With 90&deg; pointed angles, this is the standard option in our industry and by far the most popular choice among customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Rounded Cut</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Having the same right angles as the square/rectangle cut, this one comes with smooth rounded corners at &frac14;&rdquo;-&frac12;&rdquo; radius.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Outline Cut</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Design your board in whatever shape you like and choose this option so we cut it in that exact shape. Kindly bear in mind that if your design includes two pieces that are meant to be separated, you should order two separate boards. If the two pieces are in the same design, they will be connected to each other.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Overline Cut</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>This option is custom-shaped like the outline cut, but it adds an extra &frac14;&rdquo;-&frac12;&rdquo; border. The border will have the original color of the material you&rsquo;ve chosen. Remember that the border thickness will be included in the board&rsquo;s overall dimensions and not added to the original size you chose. If you want custom borders or if you want them in a color other than the basic black or white coat, you should include that border in the design and opt for outline cutting instead.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Popular Sizes for Gator Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re not sure what size would be best suited for your needs, check the most popular dimensions in the industry to help you make your choice: 12&rdquo;x24&rdquo;, 18&rdquo;x36&rdquo;, 24&rdquo;x48&rdquo;, 36&rdquo;x72&rdquo;, 48&rdquo;x96&rdquo;. Check the chart in this section for a visual comparison before ordering your gator board printing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/03/03/sizes-of-gator-board-printing.jpg\" width=\"960\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Installation Options for Gator Board Signs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This lightweight material allows for different installation methods. You can get creative, the following are a few variations we offer.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Direct Mounting</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Mount the board directly to the wall or any other smooth surface with command strips. They&rsquo;re strong enough to carry the weight of this material and they leave no residue when removed. A set of four strips can hold up to 12 lbs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Free Standing</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Use easel backs to display your product. We offer a few sizes to match your requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Hanging</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Get zip ties or suction cups with hooks to hang your custom gator board signs. You can also use ropes for this product.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5><strong>Drilled Holes</strong></h5>\r\n\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ll need holes on your board for certain mounting options. We&rsquo;ll handle that part and make your life easier by sending it with pre-drilled holes. You only need to select that option in our tool. Make sure that no important data or design elements will be cut out from the gator board printing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison Chart with Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Take a look at some similar products to discover any possible alternatives.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Gator Board Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>PVC Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Styrene Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Metal Photo Prints</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Dibond Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size range</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot; - 48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot; - 48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot; - 48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot; - 48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot; - 48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.188&rdquo;,<br />\r\n			0.5&rdquo;,<br />\r\n			1&rdquo;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.125&rdquo;,<br />\r\n			0.25&rdquo;,<br />\r\n			0.5&rdquo;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.020&quot;, 0.030&quot;, 0.060&quot;, 0.090&quot