ation page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How long do wall decals last?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>With proper care and maintenance, wall decals can last over 6 years indoors and over 3 years outdoors. To ensure longevity, avoid exposing them to intense heat, direct sunlight, or harsh weather conditions, as these may cause color fading or other deformities.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Can I put wall decals on textured walls?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Our vinyl wall decals are intended both for interior and exterior use. They will work best on smooth walls but they can also adhere to textured surfaces. This makes them a versatile option for all kinds of applications. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Do wall decals ruin paint?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Walls can be safely decorated with our custom wall decal product. No paint or other ornamental element will come off during the installation or removal of the product. Follow our custom wall decal installation steps for easy installation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to remove wall decals?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Start at a corner and peel the material of the removable wall decals away from the wall. Slowly and carefully pull in the opposite direction to prevent wall damage. If the product has been on for a long time or is on a textured surface, you might need heat to remove it. A blow dryer works great for this.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What color is the adhesive roll material?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The material is opaque white by default but full-color graphics can be applied onto it. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to make wall decals?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Go to our design platform and select the product dimensions and cutting options. Create your own wall decal online by customizing our templates or uploading and styling your own images with personalized icons, backgrounds, fonts, shapes, texts and visuals. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Where can you buy wall decals?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Our website allows you to create and order custom wall decals with unique illustrations which you can upload or create from scratch. If you’re short on ideas, you’re welcome to use our modifiable templates prepared for all kinds of purposes and occasions. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Do you ship your products?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We can ship your custom wall decal all across the UAE . Check our <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>','<h1><strong>Installation Of Custom Wall Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Use this method to attach large adhesive graphics onto walls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Wipe the surface clean using a damp cloth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Adjust its position to ensure the product is level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Fix the product with tape at the top corners and top and bottom centers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Lift one side of the product, then peel and cut off the backing paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Press the product onto the surface and smooth it with a squeegee.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Remove all the pieces of tape.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7:</strong> Lift the unbound side of the product and peel off the backing paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 8:</strong> Press the product onto the surface and go over it with a squeege</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Custom Wall Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Digital printing with quality, sun-resistant UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6”x6”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square/Rectangle, Rounded, Circle/Oval, Overline, Outline</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>52”x1,680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>White</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>48”x24”,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>12”x24”, 24”x48”, 48”x96”, custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (indoors/outdoors):</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6+ / 3+ years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',1680.00,52.00,6.00,6.00,NULL,0,0,54.568475,0.156217,NULL),(50,'Floor Decals','Pull in more foot traffic to your place of business with impossible-to-miss floor decals','https://d1xv5jidmf7h0f.cloudfront.net/circleone/images/products_gallery_images/Floor-Stickers-Decals-Signs_Clear_.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQt89f5bzZXLxRcz4UCCpN7hUPHj65zx7eCWA&s','https://www.anley.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Custom-Floor-Decals-5-800x800.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTRYnN5c2iRzYPyZz53UGL1WOLL00v03JmH-A&s','inches',2,'<h2><strong>Floor Decals Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor decals are self-adhesive graphics printed on top-quality vinyl material. At Brand Experts, you can find superior floor vinyl stickers for both business and decorative needs.  Customize them however you like and we\'ll ship them to you anywhere in the UAE. Check our <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a simple installation technique, anyone can transform their home or office floors with these peel-and-stick decals. This product is perfect for companies with limited space within their premises. Utilizing any surface area to promote your brand is an efficient way to optimize your resources. Stickers of any size will work wonders for the indoor promotion of your brand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you have empty floor space in your office? Why not use it to advance your brand? Floor decals don’t require much space and won’t interfere with the mobility of the office crew. You can display as many stickers as you wish. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>These stickers are a prime choice if you’re looking for a simple and space-saving yet effective signage solution.Reach customers, entice them when they enter your place of business and create a brand identity with eye-catching floor decals. Display these stickers in hallways, elevators, reception areas and other indoor surfaces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor decals work most effectively in high foot traffic areas by attracting passersby. While walking (especially on their phones), people tend to look at the ground. This is when the decals catch their attention. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor vinyl stickers can attract new clients or make repeat clients more aware of your business. These stickers can guide clients throughout your establishment or simply entertain them. Every feature of these floor stickers is customizable. Choose the design and the purpose of the decals and personalize them to your needs. With just a few clicks, you can create a unique design and hit the order button to get the decals shipped out the next day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Decorate your home with these simple yet attractive graphics. With an easy installation technique, you can renovate your house without any mess or tools. All you have to do is peel and stick them within minutes and that\'s it. When you don’t need them anymore, simply peel them off and wipe the surface with a damp cloth. The decals don’t leave any stains or residue, making removal a cinch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer a wide selection of free templates ready to be printed onto floor vinyl stickers. You also have the option to upload your own artwork and customize it with our design tool using a variety of elements and styles.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Social Distance Floor Decals</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As we battle the coronavirus pandemic, keeping a social distance is mandatory for conducting business in many places. By distancing ourselves from one another, we can protect each other from COVID-19. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Until the threat passes, all business owners should equip their establishments with relevant informative signs to remind and encourage people to keep their distance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Social distancing floor decals should be displayed at checkout counters, in front of entrances, between supermarket aisles and any other appropriate place to maintain safety.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Social distancing stickers can be fully customized. Display your  logo along with informative messages to provide a safe environment for your customers and employees. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>3D Floor Graphics</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>3D floor decals give freedom to the imagination. With these stickers you can display amusing, inspiring, funny and creative graphics on indoor floors. 3D floor decals can be put to decorative as well as promotional use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can get floor 3D stickers for your business floors to entertain your customers and make sure to leave an impression. Captivating 3D floor decals can be used to depict your logo, products or any message on the floor. The decals give a unique look to your space and will have a distinct impact on your audience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 3D floor graphics, you can turn any plain floor into an underwater ocean scene, a fuming lava spill or a stunning waterfall. These floor graphics are completely customizable for various venues. Anything you can imagine is possible with 3D floor decals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Floor Tile Decals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor tile decals are a fine decorating solution for homes and offices. Breathe new life into your old tiles in just minutes. Remodel your bathroom or kitchen in a quick and affordable way with vinyl floor tile stickers. Print your desired pattern on decals and apply them with a simple peel-and-stick method.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor tile stickers are the perfect remodeling option for renters. Decorate the place with your desired aesthetic then simply remove the decals when returning the property without leaving any residue.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What’s perfect about these decals is their ability to remodel your space as often as you wish without making a mess or spending a fortune. Just choose your design, get it printed, remove the backing paper and apply it to the tiles. That’s it - as simple as that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Staircase Riser Decals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Transform dull staircases into works of art with peel-and-stick decals. You can get riser decals that form a full image from the first to the last step. In this case, the image is split into the number of risers and when you step back to take a look, you will see the whole image.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Riser decals are a fast and easy way to spruce up and add a touch of personality to the stairs. The decals are very easy to apply and remove.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Floor Lettering</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Display the name and motto of your company on your office floor. Use adhesive lettering in the reception area to create a welcoming brand identity. Floor lettering can be used in malls, business centers, wedding halls and in all kinds of other establishments. Vinyl floor lettering can be used for branding as well as decorating. In our design tool, you can find a wide range of fonts and typefaces for letters to complement any interior design and thematic scheme. </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Floor Graphics for Branding</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Company branding is the key to success for many businesses. Custom floor decals are a great tool for indoor branding. As floor graphics don’t take up any space, you can use a vast amount of surface area to promote your brand. Display the name or logo of your company to highlight your presence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These attractive floor vinyl stickers work great for promotions as well. Feature special offers on the floor of supermarkets or shopping malls to attract bargain hunters. Use this persuasive technique to guide your customers where you want them to go, such as towards new products. Floor decals are a simple and economical way to attract customers and inform them in areas with good foot traffic.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Decorative Floor Decals</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor stickers are a budget-friendly choice for the decoration of any space. These stickers are perfect for providing an individual touch to your interior. Use beautiful patterns or thematic designs to decorate the floors in your space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wedding floor decals</strong> - Make your wedding day special by customizing the ceremony hall. You can display your initials on the floor or get directional floor stickers to guide everyone through hallways and aisles. Custom floor stickers can be used to decorate the hall with beautiful floral graphics or other elements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gym decals </strong>- Gyms are often equipped with floor vinyl stickers, most commonly to provide safety information but in many cases they are used for decoration as well. Floor graphics can display the logo of the gym or feature other thematic graphics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Office floor decals </strong>- Bright floor graphics create a fun and inspiring atmosphere inside the office. Offices can display their company logo on the floor along with specially themed graphics to spice up their interior. Exhibit whatever comes to mind with floor graphics - whatever you can imagine, we can transfer onto decals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dance studio floor stickers - </strong>Decorate the dance floor in your studio with our striking decals. You can showcase your collective’s name and logo or add some thematic graphics to the floor to create a stimulating environment. Our floor decals come with lamination so the printing will not wear off from constant footfall. Also, the lamination makes the decals slip-resistant so dancers can do spins and slides with the confidence that they won’t slip and fall (at least because of the floors).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Court/Arena decals - </strong>Custom floor decals are the most common branding and decoration tool for sports arenas such as basketball courts. These decals are used to brand the floors with the team’s logo and slogan. Court decals can be easily replaced per season or after each game. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the home team will host a new team for every game, the decals should be exchanged accordingly. For this case, floor graphics are the perfect choice as they are easy to apply and remove with a hassle-free installation and removal technique. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides, our custom floor signs come with lamination which is slip and scratch-resistant. So, the material is completely safe for the players and will maintain its initial look till the end of the season and beyond.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Directional Floor Decals</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom floor decals are the perfect choice for guiding potential clients to your place of business. These graphics will immediately attract everyone’s attention. People often look at the ground when they walk, making it the perfect spot for displaying wayfinding signs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Such directional decals are mainly popular and effective in the following areas detailed below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Supermarkets</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In supermarkets, floor vinyl stickers are perfect for labeling the aisles and guiding customers through them and towards the checkout. You can also label departments in supermarkets, using arrows or footprint decals to direct them to special offers. Such decals make navigating through supermarkets easier, contributing a crucial factor to enhancing the customers’ experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Retail/Department Stores</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It’s quite easy to get lost inside large retail/department stores. To make the navigation in your store easier, we recommend getting directional floor decals. These floor graphics can be displayed in front of entrances and in between aisles to label each section in a store. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Directional decals are perfect during the sales season as well. Guide customers to products and special offers with attractive stickers. You can get floor stickers in all kinds of custom shapes. Whether you want arrow decals, a pointing hand sticker or anything else, you can find them all here. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The stickers can be laminated for extra durability. This protective layer will prevent the decal from wearing off ahead of time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Warehouses</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The safety of employees in a warehouse is the number one priority. Floor vinyl stickers are a common choice for warehouse safety signs. Such floor stickers guide employees through the warehouse and make the job process safer and easier. Each section of a warehouse can be labeled using a custom floor decal. Hazardous areas should also be clearly marked with safety floor decals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can use one of our free templates, customize an existing design, or upload your own to be printed onto warehouse floor decals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Offices</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Directional floor decals are perfect for guiding customers and employees to designated office rooms, especially if the office space is large. You can get custom floor decals in arrow shapes and place them in hallways and reception areas to make navigation throughout the business center easier for everyone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Shopping malls</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can often see floor graphics in shopping malls. This is another great use of custom floor decals. Directional floor graphics in shopping malls are used to guide customers to dressing rooms, different departments and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor stickers are also used in shopping malls to direct clients to a certain store. Such directional floor decals can serve as promotional tools as well. In areas with high foot traffic, custom floor decals are a must-have solution to attract customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sun-resistant due to UV printing</li>\r\n	<li>Easily applicable and removable</li>\r\n	<li>Available in custom shapes and sizes</li>\r\n	<li>Slip and scratch-resistant due to lamination</li>\r\n	<li>Highly quality UV cured graphics</li>\r\n	<li>Space-saving, goes on any smooth surface</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor decals are made of premium-quality opaque vinyl. It’s a highly adhesive material that is easy to apply and remove without leaving any sticky residue. The material comes in rolls so you can order floor vinyl stickers in custom sizes. At Square Signs, floor graphics range from 4”x4” to 50”x1680” so you’re sure to find a size perfectly fitting your space and needs. Opaque vinyl comes in white as a default but we can print graphics in any color onto it. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Printing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You are welcome to order custom floor decals with your desired artwork and messaging. We offer full-color printing services with UV curing printers. The inks are immediately dried with ultraviolet rays, providing a long lifespan to prints. Printed floor graphics will retain their primary look and vivid colors without fading for several years with proper care. For printing, you can create your own personalized artwork with our free design tool which boasts a large selection of templates. You can also send us your own design and we can transpose it to be printed onto the decal for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cutting</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Order floor decals cut into custom shapes with our bleeding-edge digital plotter cutter. The digital plotter machine is perfect for cutting self-adhesive and soft materials such as vinyl. Its tools and knives enable ultra-precise and accurate cutting of different soft materials. A computer-controlled crop mark sensor system provides contours for cutting. Die-cutting and kiss-cutting tools are the most suitable for custom floor decals. The wide production area of our plotter cutter enables us to cut decals in a wide range of shapes and sizes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cutting Options</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Square/Rectangle</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this option, the floor graphics are cut into standard square or rectangle shapes with sharp edges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Rounded</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This option provides rounded corners to square and rectangle-shaped decals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Outline</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want your floor decals to be cut in the exact shape of your design then opt for this method.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Overline</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>By choosing this option, your floor graphic will be cut into the shape of your design with an extra white line surrounding it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lamination</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer lamination for floor decals which is the process of covering the decals with an extra protective layer. Lamination makes the material scratch and slip-resistant and gives it a longer lifespan. If you want the decals to retain their initial look for longer periods of time, you need to get them laminated. Otherwise, foot traffic will wear off the prints more quickly. We offer the following three types of lamination: glossy, matte and dry erase.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lamination Options</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Glossy</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are going for a more sheen look then glossy lamination is the right choice for you. With this lamination option, the colors on the floor graphics are more bright and vivid with a glossy finish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Matte</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Matte lamination has the opposite effect of glossy lamination. With this option, colors on the floor graphics are more subtle with a glare-free matte finish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dry Erase</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just like the afore-mentioned lamination options, dry erase lamination creates a protective layer for the decals. Additionally, it turns them into a type of whiteboard. This way, you can write on them with a removable marker and erase as often as needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Customized Design</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The floor decals we offer are completely customizable. You can send us a ready design to be printed onto the decals or you can use our free design tool with thousands of templates, backgrounds and elements to create a unique design from scratch. With our user-friendly design tool, even a child can create professional-looking graphics. With just a few clicks, you can get your desired artwork printed onto the floor stickers. In case you face any difficulties with the designing process, our team of professional designers are ready to assist you to create a stunning product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Application Surfaces</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor stickers are applicable to almost every smooth indoor surface. Before application, make sure the surface is clean or else the decal will not stick properly. For great results, we recommend applying floor decals to the following surfaces:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tile</li>\r\n	<li>Laminate</li>\r\n	<li>Hardwood</li>\r\n	<li>Indoor Concrete Floor</li>\r\n	<li>Indoor Stone Floor</li>\r\n	<li>Linoleum</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Free Ground Shipping</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We ship all our orders anywhere in the US and Canada. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts. So, if you are looking for a quick turnaround, you’re at the right place. At Square Signs, we do our best to provide our clients with custom floor decals in the fastest way possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Place your order today and your custom floor decals will be shipped to your desired location promptly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison Chart</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td> </td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Floor Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Wall Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Vinyl Lettering</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Window Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min. size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\"x6\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1\"x1\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\"x6\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max. size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>50\" x 1680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>52\" x 1680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>58\" x 1740”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>58\" x 1680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4.25mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Options</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Second Surface</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Second Surface</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Standard with no background</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Second surface with no background</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Floor Decals FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What are floor decals made of?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our floor decals are made of a highly adhesive opaque vinyl material. The material is very easy to apply and remove without leaving behind any residue. Opaque vinyl is the perfect material for displaying graphics of various color schemes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Where can I use floor decals?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Floor decals can be used in all kinds of indoor premises. The material is recommended to be applied to only smooth surfaces, such as laminate, hardwood, tile, concrete and flat stone. As for the purpose, floor decals can serve decorative as well as promotional needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can get fun floor decals to decorate the floor of your child’s bedroom. You can also use floor stickers to brand your office. Such decals are perfect for showcasing company names, logos and slogans.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Can floor decals be custom shaped?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Absolutely. Everything here is customizable. You can choose to either cut your decals in standard square/rectangle or in completely tailored shapes. Just select the “outline cutting” option in the design tool and your floor graphics will be cut in the exact shape of the design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What is the lifespan of the decals?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Depending on the amount of foot traffic, floor decals can have a life span anywhere from one month to a year or more. The laminated finish we apply to the floor graphics covers it with an ultra-thin, yet highly durable and scratch-resistant layer. In humid areas, the decals may have a shorter lifespan but in dry areas and with proper care, they can last up to three years or more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Will the graphics printed on the decal fade from foot traffic?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Short answer - no. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide lamination for floor graphics. It is a process of covering the decals with a protective layer that prevents the colors from fading and makes the material scratch-resistant. It also makes the surface slip-resistant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Will the decal ruin the floor?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>No. Floor decals do not damage any surfaces. Our floor decals are made of adhesive vinyl that is very easy to remove without leaving any stains or sticky residue. All you need to do is wipe the area with a damp cloth after removal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Can floor decals be applied in the bathroom?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, you can display floor decals in bathrooms as well. Moreover, we offer tile decals specially for the bathroom. You should have in mind that floor graphics may have a shorter lifespan due to the higher humidity levels present in a bathroom. Still, they will serve you a good few months before requiring a renovation. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Can I install the floor stickers myself?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Absolutely. Custom floor decals require a simple peel-and-stick installation. All you need to do is take measurements to find the perfect spot for application. Peel off the backing paper of the decal and apply it to a smooth surface. Then simply flatten it out to get rid of any air bubbles and that’s it. You can find a detailed step-by-step application guide in our installation section.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Can floor decals be applied to staircase risers?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, floor graphics can be applied to staircase risers. These are a perfect option for giving a fresh look to weary staircases. Just make sure to apply them to smooth surfaces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Are floor decals easily removable?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes. This is one of the advantages of floor graphics. Very little effort is needed for their application and removal. All you have to do is peel it off the floor and wipe the surface with a damp cloth. The custom removable floor decals leave no residue, so the surface will look exactly the way it did before the decal was applied.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Are floor graphics reusable?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>No, floor decals are not meant for multiple uses. Once you remove it from the floor it cannot be applied back as the material loses its adhesiveness. But if early on during the installation you want to adjust its position, you can do it by quickly peeling it off and reattaching without any issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How to clean floor decals?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In most cases, you can just clean the floors as you usually do. However, with custom floor decals, the use of harsh chemicals and abrasive cloths is not recommended in order to avoid scratches and discoloration. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Do you offer die-cut floor stickers?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, we do offer die-cut stickers. To get this result, you need to choose the “overline cutting” option in the design tool. If you don’t want an extra white line around your design, you can choose the “outline cutting” option. With this option, the decal will be die-cut in the exact shape of your design without a border.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Can I upload my own design?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, you can upload your design through our design tool. You can send us your design in any file format. Furthermore, you can make edits on your design online such as adding a text, an element or anything else.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Can I see the final design before ordering?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, you can. We have a preview option in our design tool. Just click preview when you are done with designing and you will see the final design in a full-screen mode.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How can I create a design for floor decals?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To create your design, you need to click the “Create your sign now” button in the product page. After, you will get to our free design tool where we provide all the required tools and resources to create a stunning design from scratch. In our design tool, you can find thousands of free templates in all possible categories. You can also find a large selection of backgrounds and elements that enable you to create your own design without any assistance. Once you finish the design, you can preview the final look before proceeding to checkout.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2> </h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>','<h1><strong>Installation of Floor Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom floor decals require a simple installation process. Follow the steps below for an easy and seamless application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Required tools</strong>: Squeegee (you can also use a credit card or similar object), scissors, masking tape and a damp cloth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Preparation:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before the installation, ensure the surface is clean to avoid air bubbles under the decals. Take the damp towel and thoroughly clean the area of application. Make sure the surface is completely dry. Otherwise, the material may not adhere to the surface properly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next, take a measuring tool and find the perfect spot for the installation. Adjust the decal in your desired position and mark the area of application with masking tape. (This is optional as you can install the decal without marking the application area. It just makes the process more precise so no readjustment will be necessary.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For small floor stickers:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Take the floor sticker and peel off the backing paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Apply the decal with the adhesive part to the floor and flatten it out with your hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Take the squeegee or a plastic card and pass over the decal to make sure there are no air bubbles underneath.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And you’re done.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For large floor decals:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Place the decal in the position where you want to install it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Take masking tape and place a strip down the center of the decal to hold it in place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Take one side of the decal and gently peel off the backing paper. Stop when you reach the center with the masking tape.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Take the scissors and cut off the loose backing paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Apply the exposed part of the decal to the surface and flatten it out with your hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Once the first half is installed, remove the masking tape that you used to secure the decal in its place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7: </strong>Lift the uninstalled part of the decal and slowly peel off the remaining backing paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 8: </strong>Apply the rest of the decal to the surface using the same technique.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 9: </strong>Take the squeegee or a plastic card and go over the entire floor decal to get rid of air bubbles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That’s it, you’re done with the installation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Download our PDF installation guide which provides step-by-step instructions with images on how to apply custom floor decals. Installation guides are available for all our products. Each guide provides precise information on the hardware and techniques required for application.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications of Floor Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4.25mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common sizes:  </strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12\" x 24\",  24\" x 48\", 48\" x 96\", can be customized</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.07/sqft</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Full-color printing with UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>White</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square/Rectangle, Rounded, Overline, Outline</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min. size</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\" x 4\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>With a squeegee or a plastic card</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max. size</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>50\" x 1680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1+ years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',1740.00,52.00,4.00,4.00,NULL,0,0,30.584942,0.216196,NULL),(51,'Backlit Decal Signs','Make your brand visible 24/7 with eye-catching backlit signs','https://d1xv5jidmf7h0f.cloudfront.net/circleone/images/product/Backlit_Film.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQmJJ_ZTBXO0fubjNTnzTtGWaA-kacqmQVAzQ&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQS6hZaoplwG3p0pk5nibmAUFSOKT_pgKOPww&s','https://s1-ecp.signs.com/3114/583x357/Backlit-Decals-Movie-Posters-10761.jpg','inches',NULL,'<h2><strong>Backlit Decal Signs Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit decals are an outstanding solution if you need vivid graphics for your illuminated sign that are visible 24/7. These high-quality backlit signs are used indoors as well as outdoors. They are weather-resistant and can last for years with proper care. Decals for backlit signs create a wide spectrum of colors, providing brilliant graphics that entice customers and enhance brand appeal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These signs are made with translucent vinyl decals that permit light to pass through them. The material to which the decal is applied to is also transparent so that it may be illuminated from the back. The main materials used as a base for backlit signs are acrylic, lexan, glass or other glass-like surfaces. These are transparent materials that provide perfect visibility for back-illuminated signs. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit decals are used for making light boxes, decorating storefront windows, cinema stands, shop displays and more. We offer custom backlit decals for making illuminated signs for both business and personal needs. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can create your envisioned design with our free graphic tool or choose one of our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">free templates</a>. The design you pick will be printed onto the decal with long-lasting UV protected inks. This method ensures that the print will not fade away over time, retaining its initial look for an extended period.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Custom Backlit Signs</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Signs with backlit film are applied in malls, restaurants, museums, industrial institutions or during special events like trade shows or exhibitions. Backlit logo signs are perfect for all establishments that want to get easily noticed by passersby.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are looking for a professional visual identity for your brand, backlit signs are a reliable means of branding. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>While <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/wall-decals/\">wall decals</a> are opaque, backlit signs feature a translucent material that makes the visuals glow brightly when illuminated from behind. Due to our triple-printing technique, the graphics don’t lose their vivid quality with illumination - on the contrary, they become even more striking. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit decals have photographic-quality prints and can be easily replaced if needed. The images can be applied and removed within minutes depending on the size of the backlit sign. The estimated lifespan of backlit decals is 3+ years with proper placement and care. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Square Signs provides top-quality custom light-up decals across the USA and Canada. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have the resources and expertise to provide the best-quality backlit decals in the industry. Equipped with the latest technology, we can tailor-make your decals in accordance with all your requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Features</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Translucent</li>\r\n	<li>Highly adhesive</li>\r\n	<li>Vibrant </li>\r\n	<li>Printed in full-color</li>\r\n	<li>Water-proof</li>\r\n	<li>Long lasting</li>\r\n	<li>UV-resistant</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to apply</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Custom Design</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Here at Square Signs, backlit decals are fully customizable starting at the design and ending with the buying options. You can use our free design tool to create your backlit decal from scratch. We offer an endless number of ready artwork that you can customize to your liking.  </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our thousands of free shapes, elements and backgrounds will allow you to create a stunning design within minutes. You can also upload your personal images or a ready-made design and get them directly printed on backlit decals. If you will need assistance, our professional designers are ready to help you out. Just get in touch with us and we can discuss all the details of your project.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Backlit Decal Usage </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit signs can be used for various purposes, whether business or personal. You can use backlit signs to reach out and connect with customers or create beautiful interior decor. Here are some signage ideas that can be optimized with illuminated decals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Backlit Decals for Cinema Posters</h4>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/bds-1.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit decals are often used by movie theaters to display film posters inside illuminated displays. Custom backlit signs provide the perfect visibility for cinema posters with their vivid graphics. Got an impressive home theater? We offer backlit signs for frames so that you can create the right atmosphere with your favorite movie posters.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Backlit Signs for Events</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Illuminated signs will make every event memorable. The bright colors of these outdoor backlit signs leave an indelible impression on guests. Backlit decals can be used for promotional, informative as well as decorative displays at events. Concert organizers can use backlit signs to promote sponsors or display their list of headliners. Wedding planners can use custom backlit graphics to display the images of the bride and groom or their initials. Like traditional <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-photo-prints/\">acrylic photo prints</a>, backlit signs serve various purposes at events, delivering stunning visuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Backlit Signs for Businesses</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/bds-2.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Professional backlit signs will help you get a leg up on the competition by offering irresistible graphics that will immediately capture attention. Backlit shop signs with translucent vinyl are often used for storefront branding. The backlit signs provide a constant promotion for your brand day and night. Backlit commercial signs can be a great asset to any business be it for indoor or outdoor purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3> </h3>\r\n\r\n<h4>Backlit Decals for Subway Ads</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Subways are famous for their advertising displays. These can be product promotions, movie posters, exhibition announcements and numerous other types of ads. What makes commercial subway signs so attractive is their sizable visuals that pop when accompanied by a bright light. Backlit decals are a popular choice among subway displays. The material is very easy to apply and remove which makes the process of replacement much easier. You can greatly benefit from advertising your brand through illuminated backlit signs in high traffic areas such as subways and metro stations.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Backlit Restaurant Signs</h4>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/bds-3.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Restaurants can take advantage of backlit film signs by displaying their specials, logo or entire menu. Backlit logo signs are perfect for attracting customers 24/7. There are multiple options for menu boards and one of the most effective is with the use of backlit decals. Such menus can be seen displayed both indoors and outdoors. A backlit decal will work perfectly for illuminated menus when applied to a translucent base material. The backlit film can be easily replaced when the menu gets updated. Use backlit decals with back illumination to display special offers and entice hungry customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Drive-Thru Backlit Signs</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Menu boards look dazzling when displayed indoors as well as outdoors. They’re especially effective for drive-thru restaurants and venues that operate in the evening hours. Outdoor menus are often illuminated to be visible in the dark as many drive-thrus operate late into the night and have their lights on 24/7. Backlit decals are the perfect choice for illuminated drive-thru menu displays. The medium perfectly highlights menu items with back illumination. Drive-thru restaurant owners can benefit from backlit decals as these graphics will attract more traffic when it’s dark out.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Backlit Decals for Sidewalk Displays</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Sidewalk displays are one of the most common means of outdoor advertising. Oftentimes, these displays are illuminated to provide visibility day and night. A backlit decal is the best option for these because the translucence of the material allows it to be visible in the dark when paired with lights. It ensures that attractive graphics stand out and make an impression. Backlit decals are also easy to replace so they’re perfect for displaying seasonal and holiday promotions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Decorative Backlit Signs</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/bds-4.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit decals are also a popular choice for interior decoration. You can order family or personal images printed on translucent vinyl and display it on illuminated frames to create unique home decor. You can also get a small cinema box for thematic decoration and create a home cinema vibe with your favorite movie scenes. Everything here can be individualized. Give free reign to your imagination and create custom illuminated signs with whatever backlit decals you envision.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Personalized Backlit Signs</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from all the above-mentioned types of backlit signs, you can get decals for personal purposes. Whether you use backlit signs with decals indoors or outdoors, for advertising or personal use, they’ll be sure to pique the curiosity of anyone within view. You can apply backlit decals to any transparent or translucent surface and use back-illumination to entice people with catchy graphics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Light Box Face With Backlit Decals</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to create a light box sign or change the face of your old LED sign you can get a custom lexan or acrylic face covered with a backlit decal. Lexan is a flexible and highly durable material often used for making illuminated signs. On the other hand, acrylic is a sturdy and resilient material which can serve you for years. Order a ready face replacement for your light box with custom graphics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material</strong> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom backlit decals are made of highly adhesive translucent vinyl material. The see-through material is perfect for illuminated signs. Backlit film comes in a standard white roll but you can order decals for your backlit signs in custom colors and sizes. Although the material is highly adhesive, it comes off easily without leaving any residue. The minimum size of the material is 6”x6” and the maximum size is 58”x1680”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Printing</strong> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>For translucent vinyl printing, we use premium-quality UV inks. During the decal printing process for backlit signage, special UV rays dry the inks and make the print sun-resistant. This method provides a longer lifespan to the print and protects its colors from fading. We use a special triple printing system for illuminated decals. For the first layer, we print the design, then we add a middle layer of white ink and after that, we print another layer of the design. This provides better color density and contrast to the print, giving it a unique brilliance when illuminated.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cutting</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our backlit decals are cut into custom shapes with a high-precision plotter machine. It offers faultless cuts on self-adhesive and soft materials like translucent vinyl. You can have your decals custom cut into any size and shape. The table of the plotter machine comes with a wide range of specialty tools that make it extremely fast and flexible. Thanks to its advanced toolkit, the machine ensures that your signs are cut with the highest accuracy possible. You can choose from the following cutting options for backlit decals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cutting Options</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Square or Rectangle</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this cutting option, backlit decals are cut into standard square or rectangle shapes according to the chosen dimensions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Rounded</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you prefer your square or rectangle backlit decals to have rounded edges then you should choose this option. It gives the decal a more refined appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Outline</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can choose this option if you would like your backlit decals to be cut into the exact shape of your design. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Overline</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this option, your backlit decal will be cut into the shape of your design with an extra white border surrounding it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Related Products</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/window-decals/\">Window Decals</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/perforated-window-decals/\">Perforated Window Decals</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/acrylic-signs/\">Acrylic Signs</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/static-clings/\">Static Clings</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Comparison Chart</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td> </td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Backlit Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Window Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Static Clings</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Acrylic Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min. size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\" x 6\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\" x 6\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\" x 6\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\" x 4\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max. size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>58\" x 1680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>58\" x 1680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>52\" x 850”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>96\" x 48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>3mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>7mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.125” - 0.55”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Options</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Second surface</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Second surface</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Single-sided</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Double-sided</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Second surface</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Backlit Decal Signs FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Are backlit graphics translucent?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, backlit signs are made of translucent vinyl material. Backlit decals are mainly used for illuminated signs. You can apply backlit decals to lightboxes or you can display light from behind the decal and create a custom backlit sign.  </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to install a backlit decal?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit decals require a hassle-free installation without any hardware. Pick a transparent surface and clean it for a neat application. Then take the decal and peel off the backing paper. Apply the decal to the surface and flatten it with a credit card or a special tool called a squeegee. You can find a more detailed explanation in our installation section. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to remove a backlit decal?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit decals are very easy to remove and leave no sticky residue. Just peel them off as you would a regular sticker and that’s it. Decals for backlit signs don’t leave any residue under most circumstances. If the decal has been attached to a surface for a few years then it may leave stains that can be easily removed by wiping the surface with a damp cloth.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How much does a backlit decal cost?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>There is no fixed price for backlit decals for backlit signs. It depends on the specifications of the decal. To see the price of your desired decal, you can select the size and shape in our design platform and check the price displayed on the right hand corner.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Are backlit signs sun-resistant?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, our backlit decals are sun-resistant thanks to the UV printers that we use. During the printing process, the inks are dried with ultraviolet rays which make the print sun-resistant and provide a longer lifespan for the graphics. You can display your backlit signs under the sun without having to worry about the colors fading anytime soon. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What shapes are available for backlit signs? </strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>All kinds of shapes are available for backlit signs. You can order decals for custom backlit signs with your unique design. From standard square or round shapes to custom shapes, we offer backlit signs in all possible forms and sizes. Just make sure to choose the appropriate cutting option in our design platform.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Can you help with my backlit decal design?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Sure. Firstly, we recommend using our intuitive tool for design where you can find thousands of ready illustrations and elements to help you create visuals from scratch. You can choose one of the free artworks that we offer and fully modify it to your needs. If you still need our help, you can get in touch with us and our professional designers will help you create a unique design. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How much is the shipping for backlit signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>There is no fixed shipping price for backlit sign decals. Shipping costs vary depending on the destination. You can see the price during the checkout process after you fill in the address section. We provide shipping all across the USA and Canada. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Will translucent vinyl damage the surface of the window? </strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit decals can be applied to any transparent surfaces so windows are also an option. You won’t have to worry about damage as translucent vinyl signs don’t harm or stain any surface. You can apply and remove backlit film from glass surfaces as often as needed.  </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Where can backlit signs be used?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit films can be used for various purposes. Whether you need backlit signs for promotional, decorative or other private needs, backlit decals will work wonders. The main use of translucent vinyl is for making backlit signs. Such signs can be used both indoors and outdoors. Oftentimes, translucent vinyl is used for cinema signs. Other uses of translucent vinyl graphics are for illuminated menu boards and promotional signs. You can also use illuminated decals for personal means like interior decoration.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What is a backlit decal?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit signs are made with decals from translucent vinyl. This is an adhesive material that’s used to print graphics for illuminated signs. The translucent vinyl is applied to transparent materials such as lexan, acrylic and glass. With illumination, backlit signs can provide ideal visibility at night. Backlit signs are often used for making lightboxes, movie poster displays, menu boards or any other type of illuminated signage. Backlit decals require a simple installation and can be removed almost instantly. They’re perfect for business as well as personal purposes. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Are backlit signs durable?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, backlit signs are durable and can last more than three years with proper care. The material itself is long-lasting but you can add on to their lifespan with lamination. Choose one of the three options we offer for lamination to make the surface of the material scratch-resistant. Besides that, our backlit signs are printed with UV inks, meaning that the graphics are sun-resistant and will not fade away over time. This is achieved during the backlit film printing process where the inks are dried with ultraviolet rays.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Are backlit decals laminated?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, backlit decals can be laminated optionally upon request. You can choose to get your decals either with or without lamination. We offer three types of lamination: glossy, matte and dry erase. If you want to get laminated backlit signs, make sure to choose the desired lamination option when designing your decal on our website.  </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What is decal lamination?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Lamination is an extra thin layer that protects the surface of the backlit decal material. We offer three types of lamination: glossy, matte and dry erase. The main purpose of all types of lamination is to make the material more durable by covering the surface and making it scratch-resistant. The difference between the three options is the finish. The first one is a glossy finish to enhance brilliance. The second one is a matte finish for heightening color contrast. The third one is the dry erase finish that creates a surface similar to a whiteboard. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to use a backlit decal? </strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The main purpose of our translucent vinyl decals is for making backlit signs. The decal is applied to a transparent surface such as acrylic, lexan or glass. When a light is projected from the back of the decal, the graphics become highly visible in the dark. You can use backlit decals to make backlit signs such as lightboxes, illuminated menu boards or custom cinema displays. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Do backlit decals come with lights? </strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>No, backlit decals do not have lights included with them. We don’t provide backlit signs but you can use backlit decals to create a custom backlit sign by adding string lights, bulbs, etc behind the surface. If you choose to do this, you can still replace the old graphics of your illuminated sign with new backlit decals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Are backlit decals visible at night?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The decals alone are not visible but as the name implies, backlighting is applied to make the decals visible at night. The main purpose of backlit decals is to be used with illumination to provide visibility at night. If you want to make an illuminated sign, then backlit decals are the option for graphics. You can apply the decals to transparent surfaces like acrylic or even glass and project a light behind it to make a stunning backlit sign that will be visible both day and night.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Can I use regular vinyl for backlit signs?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>No, because regular vinyl is either opaque or clear and is not meant to be used for lighted signs. Regular vinyl can be applied to walls and windows but they will not be visible in the dark even with backlights. That’s why we offer special backlit decals for illuminated signs. Our decals for backlit signs are made of a translucent adhesive vinyl and printed with a special technique. This makes the graphics visible at night when back illumination is present. So, if you want to make a custom backlit sign, you need backlit decals to achieve the desired effect.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to make your own light up sign? </strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>For making a backlit sign, you will need a transparent material such as acrylic or glass, a backlit decal and lights. Create your decal design within minutes and order your custom backlit film online. Apply the translucent vinyl onto a transparent frame or surface within minutes, arrange rear lighting and enjoy your light up sign</p>','<h1><strong>nstallation of Backlit Decal Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlit decals are very easy to install and remove without any hardware.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For application, just follow the instructions below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Before application, make sure to clean the selected surface of your backlit sign to avoid bubbles under the decal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> After the surface is clean and dry, take the decal and peel the backing paper from one corner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Apply the peeled part of the decal to the surface and start flattening it with a squeegee or a plastic card.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>Remove the backing paper little by little while simultaneously fixing the decal to the surface with the squeegee. Continue until there’s no backing tape left and the entire decal is attached to the surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5: </strong>To finish up the application, go over the decal one more time with the squeegee to make sure there are no air bubbles left. That’s it!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Uninstall</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Any kind of decal, once removed, cannot be used again as the material loses its adhesiveness. To remove the translucent vinyl, all you have to do is peel the decal off and wipe the residue, if there is any, with a wet cloth. </p>','<h1><strong>Specifications of Backlit Decal Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>3mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Material:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Backlit vinyl</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>White</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>High- resolution, UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min. size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\" x 6\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>With squeegee</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max. size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>58\" x 1680\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square/rectangle, rounded, overline, outline</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12\" x 24\", 24\" x 48\", 48\" x 96\", custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Outdoor usage:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>3+ years with proper care</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',1680.00,58.00,6.00,6.00,NULL,0,0,115.777574,0.152455,NULL),(52,'Reflective Lettering and Decals','Get reflective decals to help you display advertisements and safety guidelines. The shapes and graphics are fully customizable.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSw8B46_M7Cpj6xNNDy0qlLPf7ZCBrLSdAcvg&s','https://d1xv5jidmf7h0f.cloudfront.net/circleone/images/product/Reflective-Magnetic-signs.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSgtua5JUibivoB9cJIrlr9PtB8HJMieHyTNQ&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQ3teRSzl3dyh3K8WCKXetz1T5SbxsxwIPXFA&s','inches',NULL,'<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reflective Lettering and Decals Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you looking for adhesives that will get your messages through regardless of the time of day or night? Order reflective lettering and decals from our website. The product is made of flexible sheets that illuminate when light shines on them. They’re affordable and suitable for outdoor application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Create your reflective self adhesive vinyl decals and we’ll deliver them to your doorstep wherever you reside in the US and Canada. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Usage of Reflective Vinyl</strong> <strong>Decals</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Promotional</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Make your advertisements visible everywhere using reflective adhesive vinyl decals. Check out our reflective car decals for graphics you can use on any type of vehicle.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Informative</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>These kinds of vinyl decals are used for highlighting regulations and warnings round the clock. Find <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">sign templates</a> for your reflective vinyl lettering and decals from our collection.                                                                       </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Custom Reflective Decals Material and Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/rld-1.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We produce reflective lettering and decals with a retroreflective effect on the surface. They range between 4”x4” and 48”x1200” in size. Micro glass beads on the reflective decal bounce light back in the same direction of the source to illuminate graphics in the dark. The medium comes in 4 mil thick standard white rolls. It sticks to windows, walls and other surfaces due to high adhesiveness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our reflective vinyl printing is handled with eco-solvent inks. The images are directly applied onto the material in a thin layer. This adds a glossy finish to the product and doesn’t diminish its reflectiveness. Reflective vinyl adhesive decals are mainly used outdoors and can serve over four years.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Reflective Lettering and Decals</strong> <strong>by Shape</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our custom reflective decals can be shaped by the following cutting options:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Square / Rectangle:</strong> 90° angles with pointed corners</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Rounded:</strong> 90° angles with rounded corners</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Outline:</strong> cut in the shape of your design</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Overline:</strong> cut in the shape of your design with a border around it</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cut-out:</strong> the exact shape of your design with cut outs. This method is only available for reflective vinyl lettering.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Application of Reflective Lettering and Decals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You can install your reflective decal the same way you apply other adhesives. They stick to glass, flat walls and other similar surfaces. Visit the installation page for step-by-step instructions on how to apply reflective lettering and decals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison Chart of Reflective Decals</strong> <strong>and Simi