GcTnz5mj5fZhMRz8XKWz6PNivOTshyAc4fbJCw&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTkQQZRR1BJkHTQal-edia5ocqeOqASc49S-A&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTQx-khndnezls29sN5XAls7HWWDbwrP_2bWg&s','https://www.websticker.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/static-cling-oil-label-examples.jpg','inches',NULL,'<h2><strong>Static Clings Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Present your message on glossy surfaces such as plexiglass using our adhesive-free static clings. Capture the attention of passersby with vibrant graphics showcasing your brand name, services or working hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>No Adhesives! Reusable Graphics</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/02/28/informative-static-clings.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/sc-1.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Static clings are a popular medium intended for use on glass. They can also be applied to super smooth surfaces such as glossy laminate, varnished metal or shiny polypropylene. Unlike vinyl decals, they have no adhesives on the back. Our vinyl clings stick to the surface by a connection formed between molecular bonds and air pressure. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the material’s static properties, they can be easily applied, removed and repositioned without losing grip or leaving residue. If you’re not satisfied with the position of your graphics, all you have to do is reapply them. Our vinyl cling will serve you for a long time. Reuse this unique product as many times as you wish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">Brand Experts</a> ships its products all across the UAE. Check our <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Common Applications of Vinyl Clings</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Use custom vinyl clings to display your message on super smooth surfaces. Read further to learn about their most common uses.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Promotional Static Clings</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Vinyl clings are ideal for advertising on glossy surfaces. Turn heads towards your retail store or business with these vibrant and cost-effective graphics. Showcase your seasonal offers or branding elements with full color custom static clings. Choose a clear static cling if you want a transparent background around your visuals that allow light in. You can remove and store your graphics for future use for as long and as many times as needed. Check out our design tool to experiment with visuals and make your own static clings in minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Decorative Custom Clings</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Eye-catching and cost-effective, these custom static clings are perfect for decorative purposes as well. Use window clings to turn the interior of your spa, salon or conference center into a stunning environment. Don’t miss out on the chance to create the best first impression. To save time and get inspiration for appealing visuals, make use of our designer-made templates. </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Informative Vinyl Clings</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom static clings are striking and practical media applicable for informative usage as well. Get door clings for business to share important details about your company. Put up your working schedule, event calendars or even directions. Go for clear static clings to let some light in and while showcasing letters in any font or color. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Main Features of Custom Static Clings</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/02/28/clear-and-white-static-clings.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/16/sc-2.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our fade-resistant and reusable vinyl cling is available in different options. Here are the most common features they have.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Static Clings Material </strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our custom vinyl clings are 7 mil thick self-clinging and residue-free graphics. They come in white and clear rolls which can be printed in any color.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Clear static clings are made of a clear vinyl material. If you don’t want to cover the application surface entirely, go for this option to have your visuals on a transparent background.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>White static cling products are made of opaque vinyl rolls. White by default, they can depict images in any color. Apply these door clings for business to decorate or advertise your brand. </p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h3><strong><strong>Vinyl Clings Printing and Application Options </strong></strong></h3>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Grab the attention of passersby with our static cling printing. We offer digital, high resolution, full-color static cling printing using UV cured inks. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>These graphics are available in standard and inside-glass application options. Inside-glass application is available only for the clear option. If you want to display the image from the other side of the surface, this is the right option. Standard application is available for both opaque and clear finishes. Both self-clinging graphics are available only in a single-sided printing option.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h3><strong>Custom Clings Popular Sizes</strong></h3>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Vinyl Clings come in custom sizes ranging between 6’’x6’’ and 52\"X850\" to suit your needs. The most common sizes for the product are 12”x6”, 12”x12”, 12”x18”.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<h3><strong>Static Clings Cutting Options</strong></h3>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer two cutting options for static cling printing. Get your easy-to-apply graphics in square/rectangle or rounded cuts. The latter option can withstand more wind exposure. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please note that these graphics are not recommended for vehicles. Take a look at our <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/59\">car window decals</a> or <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/66\">custom car magnets</a> as an alternative.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison of Static Clings and Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The chart below compares our vinyl cling with similar products.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td> </td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Static Clings</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Magnetic Signs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Car Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Window Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Graphics Material:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Vinyl</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Magnetic Vinyl</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Vinyl</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Vinyl</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>7 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.030”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil, 6.3 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6’’x6’’- 52\"x850\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4”x4” - 48”x96”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\"x6\" - 52\"x1680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\"x6\" - 58\"x1680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (Indoors/ Outdoors):</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+ / 1+ years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+ / 3+ years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>N/A / 1+ years </p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6+ / 3+ years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Static Clings FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How does static cling work?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Our graphics are made of a special type of vinyl. When pressed to a glass-like surface, they adhere through a cohesive force created by a combination of air pressure and molecular bonding. As the material doesn’t contain any adhesive glues, it leaves no residue when removed and repositioned. It’s an affordable media that can be reused as often as you wish.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to apply a static cling?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Our vinyl cling is easy to apply. All you need is a clean, glossy surface and a squeegee. Check out the installation guide for easy instructions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How long does a static cling last?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Both white and clear static clings are perfect promotional media, especially for indoor applications. UV cured graphics make them fade-resistant so they can serve for over 5 years indoors. As for outdoor usage, they’ll last a year or more with proper care and good weather conditions. </p>','<h1><strong>Installation of Static Clings</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Clear and opaque static displays can be applied, removed and repositioned as often as needed. The product can be applied with a wet or dry installation method.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dry Installation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Clean and dry the application surface until it’s smooth and dust-free.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Remove the protective layer on the back of the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Properly position your graphics on the application surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Smooth it out with a squeegee or if you don’t have one, use a plastic card.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Move the squeegee from the center to the edges to get rid of any air bubbles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wet Installation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For wet installation, spray dish soap water on the back of the material as well as the area of application. Follow the rest of the steps as above. When the graphics are smoothly positioned into place, remove any excess water from the surface with the squeegee and dry it off with a microfiber cloth. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> If there are air bubbles or you’re not satisfied with the alignment, feel free to reapply the product as many times as needed.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Static Clings</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>7 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Dry mounting with a Squeegee</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.07 lbs/sq ft</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Style:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Digital, high resolution, full-color printing with genuine UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6’’x6’’</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Application Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, inside-glass (only on clear)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>52\"x850\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Shapes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square/rectangle cut and rounded cut</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12”x6”, 12”x12”, 12”x18”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (Indoor/Outdoors):</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5+/ 1+ years with proper care</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',850.00,52.00,6.00,6.00,NULL,0,0,11.934887,0.103335,NULL),(54,'Vinyl Lettering','Highly adhesive texts and graphics suitable for indoor and outdoor use. Display vibrant colors and designs with custom cut-outs.','