s. An inspirational quote or creative visual is an ideal item for home or office decoration. Explore our designer-made sign templates and restyle them to make your own product.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Informative Vinyl Letters and Numbers</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Get a straightforward directional solution by attaching vinyl lettering for signs to any glass-like surface. Apply easy-to-install texts and symbols to share safety information or regulate foot traffic. Go for a personalized design to match the surroundings.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Main Features of Custom Vinyl Lettering</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/venyl-2.jpg\" style=\"height:338px; width:600px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dash.brandexperts.ae/media/uploads/2025/02/28/storefront-vinyl-lettering_e1sELYY.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the main technical specifications of our self-adhesive graphics that make it unique and desirable.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Vinyl Lettering Material and Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom vinyl lettering is made of a self-adhesive white or clear vinyl material. They come in rolls that can be cut into elaborate shapes of any size. We use UV-curing digital printers for vinyl letter printing to ensure rich colors and a long lifespan for the graphics. </p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>White vinyl lettering </strong>- the material of the product comes in opaque white with full color graphics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Clear vinyl lettering</strong> - the adhesives are made of transparent vinyl with a second-surface printing option with a mirror image design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Frosted vinyl lettering</strong> - the product has a semi-transparent surface which is blurred from both sides.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Sticky Letters Sizes</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our custom vinyl letters are available in custom shapes and sizes ranging from 1”x1” to 58”x1,740”. Order vinyl lettering online and select the size and design that meets your needs, including custom cut-outs for tests and graphics.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Vinyl Lettering Application Surfaces</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Apply our peel and stick graphics to a wide range of nonporous surfaces. They’re suitable for window glass, but can also be applied to metal, plastic, and similar smooth surfaces. Check the installation guide for step-by-step instructions applicable for small to large products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: You can neither reuse nor reposition the graphics once they’ve been removed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Get the Shape of Your Design With Vinyl Cut Outs!</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Want to stand out with an impactful decor element? Order our vinyl cut outs and get the design of your logo or any illustration in its exact shape. The cut graphics come on a transfer tape that holds them together and allows for easy application as well safe transportation. Check out our intuitive sign design tool and bring your creative ideas to life.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison of Vinyl Lettering and Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Compare sticky vinyl lettering with similar products in the chart below.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td> </td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Vinyl Lettering</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Reflective Lettering And Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Window Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Wall Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Car Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Floor Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>4.7 mil,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>6.3 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n