ign using our intuitive online design tool. With die cut lettering, you’ll have a striking decor element that suits your visions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Where to order vinyl lettering?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Order sticky graphics on our website and get creative with our modifiable templates. With years of experience in the industry, we guarantee quality products and exceptional customer service.</p>','<h1><strong>Installation Of Vinyl Lettering</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dry Mounting</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Clean and dry the surface before application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Place the graphics in the correct position.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Remove a part of the backing paper and attach the exposed section.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Remove the rest and adhere the remaining part of the material.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Use a squeegee or plastic card to remove any air bubbles. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Work your way from the center to the edges to smooth out the adhesive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note: </strong> Remember that you won’t be able to reposition the product once attached.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Vinyl Lettering</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Material:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Vinyl</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Method:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Digital printing with fade-resistant UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Application Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, inside-glass</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.065 lbs/ft2</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Minimum Size