 both visibility and privacy. Thanks to its 70/30 ratio of opacity to perforation, a perforated window decal can display vibrant graphics on large windows. It preserves a one-way view from inside while covering up the interior from the gaze of passersby. <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/\">Square Signs</a> will help you select the best see-through window decals and deliver them across the US and Canada. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if perforated window decals qualify for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We also have standard <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/window-decals/\">window decals</a> for similar needs. Available in opaque and clear versions, they can display any message and be remodeled into various shapes and sizes. If you want to flash your promotions on-the-go, opt for <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/perforated-car-window-decals/\">perforated car window decals</a>. These adhesives are fantastic for mobile advertising needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Perforated Window Graphics by Usage</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Perforated window signs are used for a number of reasons. Keep reading to discover common uses for the graphics.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Perforated Window Decals for Advertising</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/pwd-1.jpg\" style=\"height:300px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Clear storefront windows, beauty salon doors, and stadium barriers present branding opportunities for businesses of all kinds. Whether you’re showcasing your company logo or services, custom perforated window graphics will garner the attention you want. The larger the advertisement, the more vibrant your content will be. The best part is that perforated window decals won’t block your view from the inside.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Have a concept in mind? Head over to our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\">design tool</a> and get creative with the features available in the menu. Choose templates, select elements, add texts or restyle your personal photos to create the perforated window decal you’ve envisioned.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Informative Perforated Window Decals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/pwd-2.jpg\" style=\"height:300px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides their widespread use in advertising, perforated window graphics are also suitable for informative purposes. Banks, hospitals, schools, and other institutions use these decals to display important information and notices. Thanks to their characteristic one-way vision feature, perforated window decals show vivid content from one side while maintaining a clear view from the other. Custom perforated window decals are easy to apply and peel off without leaving any residue.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Decorative Perforated Window Graphics</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/pwd-3.jpg\" style=\"height:300px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make any smooth and transparent plane look catchy with colorful self-adhering perfs. When it comes to multipurpose decoration, perforated window decals are the perfect medium. Apart from establishing privacy with appealing graphics, the material is also easily customizable. You can apply content onto a single perforated window decal, then cut it into pieces that fit the area you want. Get a perforated window decal in large dimensions, cut it into smaller forms, and adhere them in creative arrangements. Custom perforated window graphics will add appealing visuals to the exterior and block out the interior view from onlookers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Go to our collection of ready-made <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">templates</a> to spark your imagination. Pick your favorite and style it to suit your perforated window decal with just a few clicks.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Popular Sizes for Perforated Window Decals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Below are the most common dimensions for perforated window signs along with their pricing list. The prices don’t include extra options and accessories.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>15”x36”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>18”x32”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>20”x41”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>36”x72”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>48”x96”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>52”x83”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>52”x160”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Price</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$30.01</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$31.27</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$39.79</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$101.67</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$172.07</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$161.88</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>$301.71</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>* The prices in this chart may be outdated. To check the current prices and discounts for this product, please refer to the calculator at the top of the page.</strong><br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Main Features of Perforated Window Signs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Before placing your order, read on to learn about the technical specifications of our custom perforated window decals. We have premium options to satisfy your needs and expectations.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Materials and Printing for Perforated Window Decals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/11/pwd-4.jpg\" style=\"height:300px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Custom perforated window graphics are made of vinyl rolls with small, evenly spaced holes across the material. You can use your perforated window decal for all kinds of advertising and decorative purposes due to its sturdiness and versatility. Our perfs have a 70/30 opacity to perforation ratio. The frontside of perforated window signs is white to reflect the sun, whereas the backside is black to allow the viewer to see through to the other side.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor graphics, we use a UV-curing system which dries the ink while applying content onto the front face of the perforated vinyl window decals. This process makes the colors fade-resistant, preserving their vividness for up to three years.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Perforated Window Graphics by Shape</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Perforated window decals can be tailor-cut into any shape you require. Define the width and length of the application area. If it’s curved, get perforated window decals 1 inch larger than the dimensions. Afterwards, you may have to cut the extra borders with a blade to get the final fit.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe have custom perforated window decals in various shapes. Standard square or rectangle cuts as well as the rounded cut are common options. For a more striking look, you can opt for a circle or oval cut. Additionally, we can cut perforated window signs into the shape of your design, regardless of intricacy. Outline and overline-cut perforated window graphics are primarily used for decoration.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Applying Custom Perforated Window Decals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Perforated vinyl window graphics are easy to install. Mark the area where you want to apply your perforated window decal and proceed with the installation. Cut off any extra borders left over from the perforated window graphics with a blade to get a clean final look. Follow the steps below for a seamless setup.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Installation for Perforated Window Decals</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Wipe the surface clean using a damp cloth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Position the product on the window with the backing on and align it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Secure the product with tape on each side, marking the edges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Peel back 6 inches of backing and align the product with the marks on the window.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Press the product onto the surface and use a squeegee to smooth from the center outward.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Peel off the remaining backing and continue applying with the squeegee.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7:</strong> Trim any excess material with a razor or sharp knife.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 8:</strong> Use a heat gun on the product edges for better adhesion to the glass.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison Chart of Perforated Window Decals and Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The list of products below are similar alternatives to perforated window decals. The prices are for standard products without custom options and accessories.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td> </td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Perforated Window Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/frosted-window-decals/\"><strong>Frosted Window Decals</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/custom-car-window-decals/\"><strong>Car Window Decals</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/static-clings/\"><strong>Static Clings</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/vinyl-lettering/\"><strong>Vinyl Lettering</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/paper-poster-printing/\"><strong>Paper Poster Printing</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size Range</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6”x6” - 52”x1,680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6”x6” - 58”x1,680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6”x6” - 52”x1,680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6”x6” - 52”x850”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1”x1” - 58”x1,740”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td