look vibrant thanks to full-color UV cured inks. We also offer <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/custom-car-window-decals/\">car window decals</a> for advertising on-the-go.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer single-sided printing using either of the following application methods:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Standard</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The graphics are applied to the surface of the material, giving it a matte finish. With this option, your images will be oriented facing forward.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inside-Glass</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The images are mirror-printed on the surface of the material. This option is used to stick the material from the inside with graphics facing outwards.</p>','<p><strong>Wet Mounting</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This installation method helps you reposition the product on the application surface so that you can get the placement just right.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Wash and dry the window to get rid of any dust and debris.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Spray soap water on the window to help reposition the product if needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Remove the backing paper of the sticker and spray soap water on the adhesive side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Apply it to the wet window, starting from the top and moving down.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> You may glide the sticker along or remove and reapply to reposition it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6: </strong>Once in place, use a squeegee or plastic card to get rid of air bubbles. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7:</strong> Work your way from the center to the edges to smooth out the sticker.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 8:</strong> Use a soft cloth to dry the remaining water for a final application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> This method lets you reposition the product during the installation process if needed.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Clear Window Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Material Finish</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Clear and glossy with matte printing</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min Size</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6”x6”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Application Options</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, inside-glass</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max Size</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>58”x1,680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting Options</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, outline, overline, rounded</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12”x24”, 18”x24”, 36”x42”, custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation Accessories</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Squeegee</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Shape</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square, rectangle, circle, custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (Indoors/Outdoors)</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6+ yrs / 3+ yrs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',1680.00,58.00,6.00,6.00,NULL,0,0,27.001014,0.138513,NULL),(57,'Opaque Window Decals','Leverage window branding with highly adhesive and durable graphics that can be applied to windows in minutes. This eye-catching advertising medium will showcase your message where it matters most.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRE5_H6EdqYqAKRYiQUos4_T58zjZUgb2ZoUA&s','https://5.imimg.com/data5/KJ/NH/MY-8698575/window-decals-sticker-500x500.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTTAIpt393wx5s9s68zNGFBha8GqtaZQXLhEA&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSev8bPMbOiqPlDv4NRkQVpWWLs0rJ4Dw7eGQ&s','inches',NULL,'<h2><strong>Opaque Window Decals Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Take the branding and design of your business to new heights with top-quality opaque window decals. Their striking and high resolution graphics will turn heads and bring in passersby. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Durable and UV-resistant, opaque window graphics are applicable for interior and exterior use. They can showcase your brand message temporarily or for the long-term as they’re both durable and easy to replace. They’ll transform any storefront window into a constant advertising medium. Made of non-transparent white vinyl, our custom opaque window decals are also ideal for full window coverage. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Opaque Window Decal</strong><strong> Features</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>These graphics come in different shapes and sizes. Their common features are:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>- Easy Application </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>- No-Residue Removal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>- Durable Material </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>- UV Cured Printing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>- Vibrant Graphics</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Standard or front-surface printing is the only available option for this material. </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Popular Applications for</strong> <strong>Opaque Window Decal</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/window-decals/\">window decals</a> can be used for different purposes. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Promotional</strong> - Display your promotional message and reach thousands. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Informative</strong> - Use these graphics to announce campaigns and services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Decorative</strong> - Add a special touch to your windows with gorgeous graphics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Opaque Window Decals FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Can I reuse my opaque window decals?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>No, these graphics are not reusable. They lose their adhesive property once removed. See our installation guide for details.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What is the transparent alternative to opaque window decals?</strong> </h4>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/clear-window-decals/\">Clear window decals</a> are made of fully transparent vinyl. They feature clear borders and negative spaces in your design as well as see-through graphics. </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>','<h1><strong>Installation Of Opaque Window Decals</strong> </h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Application for Small Window Adhesives</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To mount small displays, note that it’s necessary to take the right measurements prior to application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Make sure to clean the surface before application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Remove the backing paper from the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Adhere the graphics to the target surface area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>Use a squeegee or a plastic card to flatten it and get rid of air bubbles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note: </strong> Remember that you won’t be able to reposition the product once attached.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>  </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Application for Large Window Graphics</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the application of large displays, you’ll need a squeegee (or any thin rigid plastic like a credit card), scissors and masking tape.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Place the graphics on the target surface with the backing paper still on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Stick masking tape down the center of the graphics to hold them in place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Step back to make sure the position meets your requirements. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>Gently peel off the backing from one side until you reach the center tape line.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5: </strong>Use scissors to cut away the loose backing paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6: </strong>Carefully attach the exposed part to the surface and flatten it with a squeegee.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7: </strong>Remove the masking tape that secures the graphics in their place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 8: </strong>Lift the unattached part and slowly peel off the remaining backing paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 9:</strong> Use the same technique to apply the second half. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 10:</strong> Squeegee going from the center out to get rid of air bubbles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note: </strong> Remember that you won’t be able to reposition the product once applied.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications of Opaque Window Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Material:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Opaque white vinyl</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.065/sqft</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Print Surface:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\"x6\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Style:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Full-color printing with UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>58\"x1680\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square/rectangle, overline, outline, rounded</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12\" x 24\", 24\" x 48\", 48\" x 96\", custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (Indoors/ Outdoors):</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6+ yrs / 3+ yrs</p>