ff starting from one corner. When finished, clean the surface with a damp cloth to get rid of any residue.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications of </strong><strong>Opaque Car Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12\" x 6\", 12\" x 18\", 18\" x 24\", 24\" x 24\", 24\" x 36\", 36\" x 54\", 48\" x 72\", 48\" x 96\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.065 lbs/sqft</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printi Surface:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6’’ x 6’’</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square/Rectangle Cut, Overline Cut, Outline Cut, Rounded Cut</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>58\" x 1,680\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>3+ years with proper care</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',1680.00,58.00,6.00,6.00,NULL,0,0,27.001014,0.138513,NULL),(61,'Clear Car Decals','Clear car decals are an innovative solution for on-the-go promotional campaigns. They’re easy-to-apply with vibrant and lasting UV-cured graphics.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSWE8qW7pAdXwzBuOCbyYWnoeNQEGJBNxEC7w&s','https://s1-ecp.signs.com/sms/Clear-Car-Decal-Hero-16083.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQcx8LsdTtgMFw3sPu83ZRSuM9xOed7xiwN5w&s','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT8D_aqa2lVeuqIBS9KTTl7r0-NWEvkkeD1Jg&s','inches',NULL,'<h2><strong>Clear Car Decals Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Looking for an elegant solution to get your message across? A clear car decal is the way to go.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Clear Window Decals for Cars</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/custom-car-window-decals/\">Clear window decals</a> are a popular type of sticker for vehicles. Adhere the clear car window decals to glass for on-the-go promotions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Clear Body Decals for Cars</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Clear car adhesives can be used on any smooth part of the car body. Turn your vehicle into a mobile advertising machine while you go about your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Shapes for Custom Clear Car Decals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our clear car stickers can be cut into the following shapes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Square / Rectangle </strong>- 90° corners</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Rounded </strong>- 90° angles with rounded corners</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Outline </strong>- cut in your design’s shape</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Overline </strong>- cut in your design’s shape with a border around it</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Materials and Printing of Clear Car Decals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A clear car decal is one of our popular <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/car-decals/\">car decals</a> made of 4 mil thick transparent vinyl. It can be applied to any part of the vehicle and last about 3 years. The product has a glossy finish with matte, UV-cured graphics. We offer single-sided prints with two application options:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Standard</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The design is printed on the surface of the material. Your images will be oriented facing forward, meaning you’ll need to stick them from outside the car.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inside-Glass</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The graphics are mirror-printed on the surface of the material. You may stick the product from inside the car with graphics facing outwards.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Clear Car Decals FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to apply clear car adhesives?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Clean the application area of any dust and debris. Peel off the backing paper and attach the sticker to the surface. Remove any air bubbles with a squeegee or plastic card.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to take care of clear car stickers?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Clean the product with a soft, damp cloth. Avoid car washes and chemical cleaners to prevent damage to the product.</p>','<h1><strong>Installation of Clear Car Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Wet Mounting</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This type of installation will help you reposition your product on the application surface to get the placement just right.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Wash and dry the area of application with a soft cloth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Spray the surface with soap water to help reposition the product if needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Peel off the backing paper and spray soapy water onto the sticky side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Apply the wet sticker to the vehicle and glide it along to position it accurately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Use a squeegee or plastic card to smooth out the sticker.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Work your way from the center to the edges to get rid of air bubbles. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Use a soft cloth to dry the remaining water for a final application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> This method lets you reposition the product during the installation process if needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Removal</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Peel off the sticker from the glass and wash the surface with soap water and a soft cloth to get rid of any residue.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications and Usage of Clear Car Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong>:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><str