e graphics damaged by abrasive brushes and chemicals. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Do you offer shipping?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, we offer shipping all across the USA and Canada for all of our products. Check our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/terms-and-policies/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts. The prices will vary depending on the size of the product and other factors. You can see the exact cost and estimated delivery date by placing your product in the shopping cart and selecting a shipping method prior to placing your order.</p>','<h1><strong>Installation of Custom Car Magnets</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Choose where on your vehicle the magnet will be applied.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Clean the area to ensure smooth application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Once the surface is clean, apply the car magnet to your desired area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That’s it, as easy as ABC.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications Of Custom Car Magnets</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.030\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Standard Sizes: </strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12”x12”, 12\"x18\", 10”x20”, 12\"x24\", can be customized</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Size Range:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\"x4\" - 48”x96”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Square/rectangle, rounded, overline and outline</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>White coated</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>3-5 years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min Magnetic Pull:</strong></p>\r