</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now let’s check out the technical specifications for this product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/04/17/td-4_6O4U62L.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Printing and Materials of Vinyl Decals for Trucks</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>brandexperts offers commercial truck decals in clear, opaque and perforated finishes. Each of them has unique characteristics so you can choose the one that suits your needs. The material of this product is made of a flexible polyvinyl chloride that’s durable and waterproof.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use state-of-the-art technology to yield full-color truck decal printing. Our UV-cured printers guarantee vibrant and sun-resistant images that will maintain their colors for an extended period of time. See below for the printing methods we employ.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check the application methods we employ below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Standard</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer a standard application option for all our custom truck decals and <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/opaque-car-decals/\">opaque car decals</a>. With this method, the graphics are directly applied on the outside of the glass.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inside-Glass</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inside-glass application allows the illustrations to be printed on the back surface of the custom truck decals. With this option, the product is applied from the inside of the glass facing outwards. This option is only available with the clear product.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Sizes</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The minimum size of custom decals for trucks is 6\"x6\" while the maximum is 52\"x1680\". All sizes come with a wide range of customization options, including creative shapes. </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Application</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Peel off the transfer paper from the back of the custom truck decals. Carefully position and attach the product to your preferred area. You can use dry or wet mounting methods for the installation of semi truck decals to big truck decals. Bear in mind that the wet mounting method can only be applied for clear decals. Find more instructions on our truck decal installation page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Cutting Options</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We use a digital plotter with computer-controlled blades that enable the precise cutting of simple to complex shapes. You can have your product cut by selecting one of the four cutting options below. </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Square / Rectangle</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Truck business decals are cut in square or rectangle shapes in your desired sizes. This cutting option is ideal for advertising mediums including <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/reflective-car-decals/\">reflective car decals</a> that can go on different types of vehicles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Rounded</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this cutting option, the custom truck decals will be similar to the standard square or rectangle form but with rounded corners. The smooth corners will give your product a more elegant look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Outline</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you choose this option, your custom truck decals will be cut in custom shapes that match the exact outline of your design. Creative shapes will give your truck a unique personality and make it stand out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Overline</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you opt for this cut,  your decals for trucks will be in the outline shape with a thin border going around it. The white overline border will emphasize the design and offer more contrast for the image colors.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Truck Decal Design</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Create truck decals online using our designer tool. Display eye-catching or professional images and information on your truck. Whether it’s for food, ice-cream or police services, you can customize the adhesives in any style. You can choose one of our free templates to modify or upload your own files for printing right away. You’re free to change every design component to produce unique results to personalize your own vehicle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Comparison of Similar Products</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong> </strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Truck Decals</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/car-door-magnets/\"><strong>Car Door Magnets</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/vinyl-lettering/\"><strong>Vinyl Lettering</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/perforated-car-window-decals/\"><strong>Perforated Car Window Decals</strong></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min. Size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\" x 6\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4\" x 4\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1\" x 1\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6\" x 6\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max. Size</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>52\" x 1,680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>96\" x 48”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>58\" x 1,740\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>52\" x 1,680”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>30 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6.3 mil</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Application Options</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>inside-glass</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, inside-glass </p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Truck Decals FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to install decals on a truck?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Remove the backing layer to expose the adhesive on your graphics. Position them carefully and apply them to the surface of your vehicle using a squeegee. The wet and dry mounting application techniques work for semi truck decals, large truck decals. Please remember that wet mounting only applies to clear custom vinyl decals for trucks. If you’re still wondering how to apply truck decals, check out our installation guide.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>How to remove decals from a truck?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>To remove the adhesive, simply pick a corner and start peeling the material off from one side. When finished, clean the vehicle surface with a soft cloth and soap water to get rid of any light residue. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What material are stickers for trucks made of? </strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>All of our company truck decals are made of premium vinyl. The material comes with different finishes based on your needs. We offer clear, opaque and perforated options. Please refer to the ‘Printing and Materials’ section above to get more details. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Are there standard sizes for custom truck decals? </strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The most common sizes requested for vinyl decals for trucks are 12”x12” and 18”x12” though the product is fully customizable. We recommend measuring the application area before making your purchase. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Will the custom truck decals fall off or scratch while driving in bad weather?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The product is highly adhesive, water-resistant and made to withstand high speeds. A good size fit and proper placement will ensure your truck business decals don\'t peel off prematurely. It should be applied to a smooth and clean surface with no cracks and paneling.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Where can I find design templates for company truck decals</strong>? </h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer thousands of free and original <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">sign templates</a> in different categories that will work for your vehicle design. Customize decals for trucks with one of our thematic templates or upload your own images and restyle them using our illustration tool. From box to mini and large truck decals to truck logo decals, we’ve got you covered.  </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>','<h1><strong>Installation Of Truck Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Dry Mounting</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This method is for quick installation. Once the product is attached, you can’t reposition it, so make sure you follow these directions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Clean the application surface of any debris.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Place the adhesive graphics in the correct position.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Fix the product with tape at the top and sides if needed to keep it in place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Remove one part of the backing paper and adhere the exposed material.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Remove the rest and adhere the remaining part of the adhesive material.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Use a squeegee or plastic card to get rid of any air bubbles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7:</strong> Work from top to bottom and center to sides to smooth out the sticker.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Wet Mounting</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The wet-mounting method provides the most accurate results as it allows you to reposition the adhesive graphics during installation. This method only applies to clear products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Wash and dry the surface to get rid of any dust and debris.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Spray dish soap water on the truck to reposition the product if needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Remove the backing paper and spray dish soap water on the adhesive side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Apply it to the wet truck surface, starting from the top and moving down.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Use a squeegee or plastic card to remove any water and air bubbles. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Work your way from the center to the edges to smooth out the material.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7:</strong> Use a soft cloth to dry the remaining water for a final application.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications And Usage Of Truck Decals</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 mil (clear, opaque)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>6.3 mil (perforated)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Digital, high resolution, full-color printing with UV inks</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6’’x6’’</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Application Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard and inside-glass</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>52”x1,680\"</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Dry or wet mounting with a squeegee</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12\"x6\", 12\"x18\", 18\"x24\", 24\"x24\", 24\"x36\", 36\"x54\", 48\"x72\", 48\"x96\", custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Usage Outdoors:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1+ years depending on weather conditions</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>',1680.00,58.00,6.00,6.00,NULL,0,0,27.001014,0.138513,NULL),(69,'Truck Window Decals','Our truck window decals are applicable for all types of large vehicles. They’re available in various shapes and designs.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71w0WRKfofL._AC_UF894,1000_QL80_.jpg','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?