. Both products will give your booth a neat look by exponentially increasing your branding’s visibility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check out our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/trade-show-table-covers/\">trade show table covers</a> if you’re looking for an event-specific product.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Custom Stretch Table Covers</strong> <strong>for Job Fairs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Prepare your booth for the upcoming job fair by adorning it with printed stretch table covers. You can spruce it up with other marketing items such as <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/retractable-banners/\">retractable banners</a> and <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/step-and-repeat-banners/\">step and repeat banners</a>. This combo will effortlessly grab the attention of passersby.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Personalize and design your <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/custom-signs/\">custom signs</a> from scratch with a few clicks of your mouse.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Stretch Tablecloths</strong> <strong>for Conferences and Conventions</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A stretch table cover with logo illustrations is a must when it comes to conventions and similar business events. For a smart design solution, you can add <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/product/custom-table-runners/\">custom table runners</a> with contrasting visuals over the cover.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Specifications of Stretch Table Covers</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Explore this product’s specifications and place your order based on all the cool features it provides. Create your own custom stretch table cover from scratch using our <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/designer/\">sign design tool</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Custom Stretch Table Cover</strong> <strong>Material</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We use 8.8 oz stretch tension fabric to create high-end stretch table covers. The warp knit material allows this product to stretch without affecting its elasticity or the visuals’ vibrancy.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Stretch Tablecloth</strong> <strong>Sizes</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer two standard sizes for custom stretch table covers.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Table Sizes</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Product Sizes</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6ft tables</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>135.75”x92.68”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>8ft tables</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>159.75”x92.67”</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Custom Stretch Table Cover</strong> <strong>Printing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We apply a dye sublimation printing technique to create our custom printed stretch table covers. Thanks to this method, the ink penetrates into stretch fabric giving the illustrations a vibrant matte finish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Browse through our large collection of <a href=\"https://www.squaresigns.com/templates/\">sign templates</a> to find a design that fits your needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Application of Custom Stretch Tablecloths</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It’s easy to set up a branded stretch table cover. Follow these steps for a precise application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Remove your cover from its package and unfold it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Place it on the tabletop and adjust its orientation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Spread it on the tabletop and stretch the product down the legs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Pull the corners of the product down and wrap them under the table’s legs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Comparison Chart of Stretch Table Covers</strong> <strong>and Similar Products</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Take a look at the chart below to compare custom stretch table covers and similar products. The pricing corresponds to products that come with default options and without add-ons.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td> </td>\r\n