>Step 5:</strong>&nbsp;Press and hold for a few seconds until they&rsquo;re securely attached.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications And Usage Of Gold Acrylic Signs</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thickness:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1/8&quot; or 0.125&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Material Finish:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Reflective gold with matte printing</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Weight:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>0.750 lbs/sq ft</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Drilled Holes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4 corners, top and bottom center, top corners only, 4 corners and top and bottom center, right &amp; left center drilled holes</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Min Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&quot;x4&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Printing Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, single-sided</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Max Size:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>48&quot;x96&quot;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Cutting Options:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Standard, outline, overline, rounded</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Common Sizes:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>18&rdquo;x24&rdquo;, 19&rdquo;x27&rdquo;, 20&rdquo;x30&rdquo;, 27&rdquo;x40, custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Installation:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Silver or gold standoffs, suction cup and hook, command strips,&nbsp;easel backs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Shape:</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Rectangle, circle, square, custom</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lifespan (Indoor/Outdoor):</strong></p>