 a variety of shapes. While the word &ldquo;custom&rdquo; implies that you have freedom with your design, there are popular forms accepted in the industry that you can opt for using our&nbsp;design tool. Explore some of the style options below for inspiration.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Regular Landscape / Portrait Acrylic Displays</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Landscape simply refers to pictures on acrylic that have a horizontal orientation, whereas portraits have a vertical orientation. We offer landscape and portrait acrylic glass pictures of custom sizes and edge options.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Panoramic Acrylic Prints</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Panoramic format, just like landscape, has a horizontal orientation. However, it mostly refers to a higher ratio between the height and width of your acrylic decor. This format is perfect for wide-angle photos of cityscapes, naturescapes, and similar imagery.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Square Acrylic Decor</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Brand Experts give pictures on acrylic a neat and polished touch. Get multiple prints in different sizes to combine into a geometric collage on your living room wall. You can also align acrylic glass photo prints in one row to decorate the lobby or hallway of your office, restaurant, or hotel.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Round Acrylic Photo Prints</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Circular or oval acrylic pictures have an even more unique appearance for various uses. Go with large acrylic photo prints with a circle or oval shape to create a focal point and visual hierarchy in your overall design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Acrylic Photo Prints by Size And Thickness</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Popular acrylic photo print sizes displayed with beautiful cityscape images.\" height=\"609\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/01/popular-sizes-of-acrylic-photo-prints.jpg\" title=\"Popular sizes of acrylic photo prints\" width=\"1084\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer custom-size acrylic glass prints ranging from 4x4 to 96x4