plications. <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/9\">Styrene signs</a> are made of scratch-resistant plastic that’s durable enough to withstand bending, abrasion and harsh weather conditions. The medium is more flexible but similar to <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/7\">PVC signs</a> due to a smooth surface ideal for high-resolution printing. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">Brand Experts</a> provides shipping all over the UAE. Check our <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/\">terms and policies page</a> to see if this product qualifies for special offers or shipping discounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Styrene Poster Printing And Material</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Styrene posters are made from styrene, a flexible type of plastic that can be recycled. Like <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/102\">acrylic photo prints</a>, they’re durable, lightweight and great for displaying vibrant graphics. The material is ideal for trade show booths, wall decorations, restaurant menus, and store advertisements. This product comes in 0.020″ and 0.030″ thicknesses. You can choose command strips, a suction cup and hook or zip ties with grommets for installation. For step-by-step instructions, see our styrene posters installation guide.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Styrene posters look fantastic with full color HD printing. We use long-lasting UV cured inks that  will keep their vibrancy for many years to come. Single and double-sided printing options are available. Weatherproof and scratch-resistant, styrene poster printing is a durable alternative to <a href=\"https://www.brandexperts.ae/product/14\">paper poster printing</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Use our online design tool and choose from thematic templates to modify or create your design from scratch. Our platform is feature-rich and simple to use so you can bring your vision to life in minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Styrene Poster Shape Options</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide the following shapes for this product:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Square / Rectangle</strong> - cut with 90° corners</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Rounded</strong> - 90° angles with rounded corners</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Outline</strong> - cut in the exact shape of your design</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Overline</strong> - cut in your design’s shape with a border around it</p>\r\n\r\n<h3> </h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Styrene Posters FAQ</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What are styrene poster displays used for?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>This product is suitable for a wide range of applications, including displays for trade shows, promotions, branding and decoration. </p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Can styrene posters be used outdoors?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The product is intended for indoor settings but it\'s also applicable for outdoor use with a lifespan of 3+ years.  </p>','<h1><strong>Installation Of Styrene Posters</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Installation With Command Strips</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Command strips are the best option for direct mounting without visible hardware.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Remove the cover from the adhesive part on one side of the strips.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Apply the strips with the exposed adhesives to the back of your display.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Remove the cover from the other side of the adhesives on the strips.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>Attach your display to the wall by pressing the areas with strips against it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5: </strong>Grab the base of the display and gently pull it away from the wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6:</strong> Unbind the command stips from each other and set the product aside.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 6: </strong>Allow the strips to bind to their respective surfaces for at least one hour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 7: </strong>Attach your display back onto the surface by reattaching the strips.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Removal of Command Strips</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Command strips can be easily removed without leaving any residue behind. They lose adhesive property and are not reusable after you peel them off.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Grab the bottom corners of the display and pull away from the wall to detach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Pull the tab of the adhesive strips off the wall until they come off.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Installation With Suction Cup & Hook</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The suction cup and hook is an ideal option to hang your display from glass or other smooth surfaces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Choose a clean, dust-free and smooth surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Stick the suction cups by pressing them to the application area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Pass the hooks through the pre-drilled holes on your display.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Installation With Zip Ties</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ideal for a hanging installation of displays that have grommets. You can select them as an option from our design menu. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Choose the number of zip ties according to the number of grommets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Pass the zip ties through the grommets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Attach the zip ties to the installation area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 4: </strong>Tighten all the zip ties for a firm grip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 5: </strong>Cut off all the extra ends of the zip ties for a clean look.</p>','<h1><strong>Specifications And Usage Of Styrene Posters</strong><strong> </strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>This product is ideal for business branding, restaurant menus and store promotions as well as trade show booth, office and home decor. Its bendable and durable features give it versatility for displays of different shapes and sizes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Digital printing with UV inks</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Thick