n\r\n<p>If you&#39;ve decided on purchasing acrylic signs, it&#39;s important to learn about their features and variations to select the one that suits your needs best. The products offer excellent image protection and impressive longevity, particularly indoors. When used outdoors, acrylic signs are still highly resistant to direct sunlight, thanks to our UV inks.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThese products are available in transparent, opaque, and reflective options, and boast exceptional durability. The material is impact- and moisture-resistant, weighing half as much as glass. With 92% light transmission, it&rsquo;s also more shatter-resistant than glass, being 17 times stronger. You can choose between three thicknesses: ⅛&rdquo; (all), &frac14;&rdquo; (clear, white, black, frosted), and ⅜&rdquo; (clear).</p>',48.00,96.00,4.00,4.00,NULL,0,0,212.440817,0.255611,NULL),(118,'Window Decals','Highly adhesive window graphics for promotional and decorative purposes. Choose the type that best satisfies your needs.','https://brand-experts.b-cdn.net/dummy-products/all-types-of-window-decals.jpeg','https://brand-experts.b-cdn.net/dummy-products/custom-window-decals.jpeg','https://brand-experts.b-cdn.net/dummy-products/outdoor-window-decals.jpeg','https://brand-experts.b-cdn.net/dummy-products/window-decals.jpeg','inches',NULL,'<h2><strong>Window Decals Overview</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Reach a larger audience by displaying superb custom window decals with sophisticated designs. Pick your choice from the wide array of our window decal signs that work great for business and personal needs. Thanks to its versatility and premium quality, this medium serves a number of promotional and decorative purposes. Explore the advantageous features of our glass decals below:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Durable Material</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easy Application</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Residue-Free Removal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>UV-Cured Graphics</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Long Life