new heights. The durable 70lb. paper thickness provides durability while maintaining a sleek, high-quality feel. Every detail, from material to printing, works together to produce notepads that are as functional as they are visually impressive.</p>',11.00,8.50,5.50,4.25,NULL,0,1,313.411150,5.905851,NULL),(132,'Postcard Printing','At Brand Experts, We craft custom printing solutions to make your brand shine with vibrant designs. These products are available in packs of 100, 250, 500, and 1,000.','https://brand-experts.b-cdn.net/dummy-products/postcard-printing-golden-vine-estates.jpeg','https://brand-experts.b-cdn.net/dummy-products/postcard-printing-green-wedding.jpeg','https://brand-experts.b-cdn.net/dummy-products/postcard-printing-natural-travel-landscape.jpeg','https://brand-experts.b-cdn.net/dummy-products/postcard-printing-swimming-academy.jpeg','inches',12,'<h2>Postcard Printing Overview</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Brand Experts offers custom postcard printing designed to make your brand’s message unforgettable. Imagine a postcard that’s not just mail, but a mini-masterpiece, something people will notice, remember, and hold onto. Our custom postcard printing is perfect for businesses looking to add a personal, high-impact touch to their communication, incorporating vibrant colors, premium materials, and full customization. Each postcard speaks to your brand’s unique identity in a way that digital communication just can’t match, whether it’s a product announcement, a seasonal greeting, or a friendly reminder. Use our extensive range of templates and bring your ideas to life with postcards personalized with our design tool that are memorable moments in the hands of your audience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Benefits Of Custom Postcards</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/setup_3g9MbQg.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:32px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/lightweight-icon-1.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:32px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lightweight</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/impactful_3OgWZWf.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:32px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Impactful</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/memorable_Js8Qnjy.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:32px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Convenient</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/professional-1_70jE18Z.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:32px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Professional</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Types Of Custom Postcards</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/postcard-printing-standard-wedding-card.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Standard Postcards (6\"x4\")</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our standard postcards are versatile and crafted from durable materials to make a strong impression. Available in two thicknesses - 14-point and 16-point - they offer full-color printing options and a glossy front that adds a polished, eye-catching finish. You can choose between single-sided or double-sided printing, allowing you to create postcards that capture your brand\'s style with a professional, high-quality look that’s sure to stand out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/postcard-printing-color-core-nature.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Color-Core Postcards (5.5\"x4.25\")</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Color-core postcards bring a unique, stylish edge to your messaging with vibrant, colored borders that make each card pop. This custom postcard printing is made from durable 36-point thick material built for a bold look that speaks to quality. We offer full-color printing with a matte finish on both sides. Choose from striking edge colors like aqua, black, blue, orange, and red which create an accent that enhances your brand’s personality and leave a memorable impression.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/postcard-printing-foldover-blue-medical.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Foldover Postcards (10.25\"x7\")</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Foldover postcards provide an ideal solution for those looking for extra space. These postcards are crafted from 16-point thick material with a gloss-coated front and can be printed in full color on the outside only or on both the outside and inside, giving you ample room for design and messaging. Foldover postcards are perfect for detailed information and announcements that require more space, all while maintaining a sleek, professional appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Use Cases For Custom Postcard Printing</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/postcard-printing-business-conference.jpg\" style=\"height:375px; width:500px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Corporate Postcards</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Just like custom brochures, corporate postcards are a powerful, versatile tool for business communication, helping companies make meaningful connections with clients, partners, and prospects. Postcards offer a tangible, personalized way to deliver your brand’s message directly into the hands of your audience, as opposed to digital messaging. They’re ideal for a range of business purposes, corporate postcards can enhance marketing strategies, build client relationships, and elevate brand recognition with every mailing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/postcard-printing-travel-photo.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Travel Postcards</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Travel postcards capture the essence of a destination, perfect for both tourism marketing and personal use. Businesses like hotels, tour operators, and travel agencies can use them to promote destinations, highlight exclusive packages, or provide guests with a memorable keepsake. For travelers, postcards offer a personal way to share journey highlights with friends and family. Physical postcards inserted into custom envelopes become cherished keepsakes loved ones can display and remember, making it a timeless way to connect across distances.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/postacard-printing-merry-christmas.jpg\" style=\"height:375px; width:500px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Holiday Postcards</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Holiday postcards add a festive, heartfelt touch to any message, making recipients feel valued and appreciated. Businesses can send seasonal greetings, holiday promotions, or thoughtful year-end updates paired up with custom notepads that reinforce customer relationships. These custom postcards make a memorable impact during the holiday season. For individuals, holiday postcards allow them to share warmth and cheer with family and friends. This touch of festive spirit makes holiday postcards a wonderful way to connect and celebrate the season.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Specifications Of Custom Postcards</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/printing-icon-1_klAukPn.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:32px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full-Color Flat Printing</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/thickness-icon-1_DX6PxbS.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:32px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thickness</p>\r\n\r\n<p>14 pt. - 16 pt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/size-2_zbnKEPC.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:32px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sizes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.5\"x4.25\", 6\"x4\", 10.25\"x7\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/quantity-737282_N50iOpj.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:32px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantities</p>\r\n\r\n<p>100, 250, 500, 1,000</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/uploads/2025/03/04/postcard-printing-material-architectural.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Material and Printing of Custom Postcards</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our custom postcards are designed with premium paper and sharp, vibrant printing that brings your message to life. Available in sturdy 14-point,16-point, and 36-point cardstock, our custom postcards offer both gloss and matte finishes. The glossy option amplifies color and gives a sleek, polished look, while matte provides a smooth, elegant feel. Each postcard is printed in high-resolution full color o